\id 1CH
\h 1 Thusimbu
\toc1 Thusimbu Khatna
\toc2 1 Thusimbu
\toc3 1 Thusimbu
\mt1 1 CHRONICLES
\mt2 THUSIM BU KHATNA
\mt3 1 Chronicles Sung Thu Umdan
\ip 1 Chronicles lekhabu akon hin Pathen'in Israel te chunga thil agon-toh dan muchet ahi. Hiche lekhabu’a kon hin Pathen chate ihi-nau photchetna tampi aum'inahi. 1 Chronicles lekhabu kipatna lang hi, insung khat thingphung banga kisong Adam in akipan in—hiche hin Pathen dinga lhen-tum insung khat chule thusim hi akimatna aum sohkeijin ahi. Bung phabep, tichu (Bung 10) sunga hin, Saul lengpan vai ahin hom in, adang bung amoh chengsea hin David lengpa in Israel tedinga abolthei sun abol in, chule achai-nan David thi thudol aum'inahi. Bung khat apat bung ko sunga hin Pathen tohgon dungjui’a Israel te agam uva ahung kinung le nau thudol aseijin; chule David in atoh ding Israel mite alam kaijin Pathen ahou khom un ahi.
\is1 Lekhabu Jihpa Chule Akijih Kum
\ip Juda te chondan toh kilhonin 1 Chronicles hi Ezra Themgao jih ahiti, aki cheh in ahi.
\ip Hichu 450-400 BC sunga anajih ahi.
\is1 Lekhabu Hi Koi Henga Chule Itih Phatlai Thusim Ham?
\ip Israel mipite jouse dinga ana jih ahi. 1 Chronicles hin khanggui thusim akipatna’a pat Babylon aum geiju thudol asei in ahi. Chule bung som le khat apat achaina chan hi David lengpan lengvai apoh thudol aseijin ahi. David chu ama le ama akingaiton, Pakaiyin ama chu Israel chate chunga lenga atundoh mong mong ahitai ti, ahedoh tan chule ama lenggam chu amite khohsah jal’in akichoi sang lheh jeng tai (14:2).
\c 1
\s1 Adam Son Achilhahho
\p 
\v 1 Adam son le achilhahho Seth, Enosh;
\v 2 Kenan, Mahalaleh, Jareh,
\v 3 Enoch, Methuselah, Lamech,
\v 4 Chule Noah, Noah chate ho * Shem, Ham chule Japheth.
\v 5 Japheth chilhahho chu Gomer, Magog, Madai, Javan, Tubal, Meshech, chule Tira ahiuve.
\v 6 Gomer son achilhahho chu Ashkenaz, riphath * chule Togarmah ahiuve.
\v 7 Javan son achihlhahho chu Elishah, Tarshish, kikttim chule Rodanim ahiuve.
\v 8 Ham chapa te chu Cush, Mizraim, *Put chule Canaan ahiuve.
\v 9 Cush son achilhahho chu Seba, Havilah, Sabtah, Raamah, chule Sabteca ahiuve. Raamah chapa te ni chu Sheba le Dedan ahi lhon'e.
\v 10 Cush jong hin Nimros ahingin, Nimros hi leiset chunga galhang masapen in ahung pang tai.
\v 11 Mizraim hin Ludim toh, Anamim toh, Lehabim toh, Naphtuhim toh,
\v 12 Pathrusim toh, Casluhim toh, Caphtorim toh ahingin, amaho’a konna hi Philistine ho hung kondoh ahiuve.
\v 13 Canaan chapa masapen/tahpen chu Sidan ahin, Sidon chu Sidon mite ahung pen nau bulpi ahung hitai. Chujouvin Canaan in Heth kitipa chu ahinge.
\v 14 Jebus mite, Amor mite, girgash mite,
\v 15 Hivi mite, Ark mite, Sin mite,
\v 16 Arvad mite, Zemar mite, chule Hamath mite jong ahiuve.
\v 17 Shem chapa te chu Elam, Asshur, Aphaxad, Lud, chule Ram ahiuve.
\v 18 Arphaxad kitipa hin Shelah ahingin, Shelah kitipa hin Eber ahinge.
\v 19 Eber hin chapa ni ahingin, chapa masapa chu amin Peleg akiti ( hichu kikhentel tina ahi ); ijeh-enem itileh ama khang laiya leiset mite chu pao le ham chom chom’a kikhentel anahi, chule asopipa min chu Joktan ahi.
\v 20 Joktan hin Almodad, Sheleph, Hazarmaveth, Jerah,
\v 21 Hadoram, Uzal, Diklah,
\v 22 Obal,*Abhimael, Sheba,
\v 23 Ophir, Havilah, chule Jobab ahingin ahi. Mi hichengse hi abonchauva Joktan son achilhah jeng ahiuve.
\v 24 Shem son achilhah : Arphaxad, Shelah, *
\v 25 Eber, Peleg, Reu,
\v 26 Serug, Nahor, Terah,
\v 27 Chule Abram, ama hi khonunga Abraham kitipa chu ahi.
\v 28 Abraham chapa teni chu Isaac le Ishmael ahi lhon'e.
\v 29 Akhanggui kisim dan’u chu hiti hi ahiye :
\p Ishmael chapa te chu Nebaioth ( apeng masapen ), Kedar, Adbeel, Mibsam,
\p 
\v 30 Mishma, Dumah, Massa, Hadad, Tema,
\v 31 Jetur, Naphish, chule Kedemah ahiuve. Hichengse hi Ishmael chapa te ahiuve.
\v 32 Abraham thaikemnu Keturah chapa te chu Zimran, Jokshan, Medan, midian, Ishbak, chule Shuah ahiuvin ahi. Jokshan chapa te ni chu Sheba le Dedan ahi lhon'e.
\v 33 Midian chapa te chu Ephah, Epher, Hanoch, Abida, chule Eldaah ahiuve. Mi hichengse hi Abraham thaikemnu Keturah son achilhah jeng ahiuvin ahi.
\v 34 Abraham hin Isaac anahingin ahi. Isaac chapa te ni chu Esau le Israel* ahi lhon'e.
\v 35 Esau chapa te chu Eliphaz, Reuel, Jeush, Jalam, chule Korah ahiuve.
\v 36 Eliphaz chapa te chu Teman, Omar, Zepho, Gatam, Kenaz chule Amalek ahiuve. Amalek hi Timna sung peng ahi.
\v 37 Reuel son achilhaho chu Nahath, Zerah, Shammah, chule Mizzah ahiuvin ahi.
\v 38 Seir son achilhahho chu Lotan, Shobal, Zibeon, Nah, Dishon, Ezer, chule Dishan ahiuve
\v 39 Lotan chapa te ni chu Hori le Heman ahilhonin, chule Lotan sopinu min chu Timna akiti.
\v 40 Shobal son achilhahho chu Alvan, *Manahath, Ebal, Shepho,* chule Onam ahiuve.
\p Zibeon chapa te ni chu Ariah le Anah ahi lhon'e.
\p 
\v 41 Anah chapa chu Dishon ahin; Dishon chapa te chu Hemdan, * Eshban, Ithran, chule Keran ahiuve.
\v 42 Ezer chapa te chu Bilhan, Zaavan, chule Akan * ahiuve.
\p Dishan chapa te ni chu Uz le Aran ahi lhon'e.
\p 
\v 43 Israel te chunga mi koima lengvaipoa pang anaum masanga Edom gamsunga lengvaipoa anapang miho chu leng hichengse hi ahiuve.*
\p Boer chapa Bela ahin, a lengvaipohna khopi min chu Dinhabah akiti.
\p 
\v 44 Bela athi phat in ama khel’in Bozrah kho’a mi Zerah chapa Jobab chun lengvai anapon ahi.
\v 45 Jobab athi kit phat chun ama khel’in Teman mite gamsunga mi Husham kitipa chun lengvai anapon ahi
\v 46 Husham athi phat’in ama khel’in Moab gamsunga midan sepaite kisatpia jou lengpa Bedad chapa Hadad chun akhopi min Avith kiti munna kon chun lengvai anapon ahi.
\v 47 Hadad athi kit phat chun Masrekah khoa mi Samlah chun ama khel’in lengvai apotai.
\v 48 Samlah athi phat’in ama khel’in luipi dunga cheng Rehoboth khoa mi Shaul kitipa chun lengvai apotan ahi.
\v 49 Shaul thi nungin ama khel’in Acbor chapa Baal-hanan kitipa chun lengvai apon ahi.
\v 50 Baal-hanan athi kit phat’in ama khel’in Hadad chun akhopi min Pau kiti munna kon chun lengvai anapon ahi. Ajinu min chu Mehetabel ahin, Matred chanu chule Me-zahab tunu anahi.
\v 51 Hadad jong athi kit tai.
\p Edom gam'a ahung lamkai/haosa ho chu Timna, Alvah,* Jetheth,
\p 
\v 52 Oholibamah, Elah, Pinon,
\v 53 Kenaz, Teman, Mibzar,
\v 54 Magdiel, chule Iram ahiuve. Mi hichengse hi Edom gam'a phung lamkai ( Haosa ) jeng ahiuvin ahi.
\c 2
\s1 Israel Chate
\p 
\v 1 Israel chapa te chu Reuben, Simeon, Levi, Judah, Issachar, Zebulun,
\v 2 Dan, Joseph, Benjamin, Naphtali, Gad, chule Asher ahiuve.
\v 3 Judah chun Canaan numei nu Bathshua kitinu a kon'in chapa thum ahingin ahi. Amaho min chu Er, Onan, chule Shelah ahiuve. Achapa apeng masapa Er kitipa hi Pakai mitmun agilou behseh jengin ahileh Pakaiyin jong amapa chu athat tai.
\v 4 Judah hin amounu meithainu Tamar chu toh jong chapa pengkop ni Perez le Zerah chu ahing kit’in, hijeh chun Judah hin chapa nga jen aneiyin ahi.
\v 5 Perez chapa te ni chu Hezron le Hamul ahi lhon'e.
\v 6 Zerah chapa te chu Zimri, Ethan, Heman, Calcol, chule Darda ahiuvin mi nga jeng alhing uve.
\v 7 Carmi ( Zimri son achilhah ) chapa chu Achar ahin, ama hin suhmang dinga kikoisa thet ho chunga Israel te anabol gim lheh jengin ahi. \x + \xo 2:7 \xt Joshua 7:1\x*
\v 8 Ethan chapa chu Azariah ahi.
\v 9 Hezron chapa te chu Jerahmeel, Ram, chule Caleb* ahiuve.
\v 10 Ram hin Amminadab ahingin, chule Amminadab hin Judah te leng chapa Nahshon ahingin ahi.
\v 11 Nahshon hin Salmon ahingin, Salmon hin Boaz ahingin,
\v 12 Boaz chun Obed ahingin, Obed in Jesse ahinge.
\v 13 Jesse chapa apeng masapaen chu Eliab ahin, anina pa Abinadab ahin, athum lhinna pa Shimea ahin,
\v 14 Ali lhin na pa chu Nethanel ahin, Raddai chu nga lhinna ahi.
\v 15 Ozem chu achapa gup lhinna ahin, chule asagi lhinna chu David ahitai.
\v 16 Amaho hin sopi numei ni aneiyun amin lhon jong Zeruiah leh Abigail ahi lhon'e. Zeruiah hin chapa thum ahingin, Abishai, Joab, chule Asahel ahiuve.
\v 17 Abigail hin Ishmael mi Jether kitipa chu ahing lhonne.
\v 18 Hezron chapa Caleb jong hin ajinu Azubah kitinu Jerioth khoa minu chu toh chapa phabep ahing lhonin ahi. Amanu chapa te chu Jesher, Shobab, chule Ardon ahiuvin ahi.
\v 19 Azubah hi athi nungin Caleb in Ephrathah akichenpi’in, chule chapa khat Hur kitipa chu ahing lhonne.
\v 20 Hur hin Uri ahingin, Uri in Bezalel ahinge.
\v 21 Hezron hin akum kum som gup jen alhin nungin, Gilead sopinu Makir chanu chu akichenpin ahileh, chapa khat amin Segub kitipa chu ahing lhonnin ahi.
\v 22 Segub hin Gilead gamsunga khopi somni le thum jen semdoh’a chule lengvaipoa pang Jair kitipa chu ahingin ahi.
\v 23 Ahin Geshur le Ram chun Jair ngahmun khopi toh Kenath khopi toh chule akhobah chengse kho lehn cheh somgup jen alah tha lhon tai. Mi hichengse hi Gilead hingpa Makir son achilhah jeng ahiuvin ahi.
\v 24 Hezron chu Caleb-Ephrathah ngahmun khopia athi nungin ajinu Abijah chun chapa khat Tekoa hingpa Ashhur kitipa chu ahinpeh-in ahi.
\v 25 Hezron chapa apeng masapen Jerahmeel chapa te chu apeng masapen Ram ahin, Bunah ahin, Oren ahin, Ozem ahin, chule Ahijah ahiuve
\v 26 Jerahmeel kitipa hin ji chom khat jong aneiyin, amin chu Atarah akiti. Amanu hin Onam chu anahinge.
\v 27 Jerahmeel chapa masapen Ram chapa te chu Maaz, Jamin, chule Eker ahiuve.
\v 28 Onam chapa te ni chu Shammai le Jada ahilhonnin, chule Shammai chapa te ni chu Nadab le Abishur ahi lhon'e.
\v 29 Abishur le ajinu Abihail chapa te ni chu Abhan leh Molid ahi lhon'e.
\v 30 Nadab chapa te ni chu Seled le Appaim ahi lhon'e. Seled chu cha nei louvin athitan,
\v 31 Ahin Appaim hin chapa khat amin Ishi kitipa chu aneiyin ahi. Ishi chapa chu Sheshan ahin, chule Sheshan chapa chu Ahlai ahi.
\v 32 Shammai sopipa Jada chapa te ni chu Jether le Jonathan ahi lhon'e. Jether hi cha nei louvin athitan,
\v 33 Hinlah Jonathan hin vang chapa ni Peleth le Zaza ahinge. Mihem hijat hi Jerahmeel son achilhah ahiuve.
\v 34 Sheshan in chapa te aneipon, ahin chanu tampi ahinge Sheshan hin Egypt mi pasal khat soh aneiyin, amin jong Jarha akiti.
\v 35 Sheshan in hiche asohpa Jarha kitipa hi achanu khat toh akichensah in ahileh achanun amapa chu toh chapa khat amin Attai kitipa chu ahing lhone.
\v 36 Attai hin Nathan ahingin, Nathan in Zabad ahinge.
\v 37 Zabad hin Ephlal ahingin, Ephlal chun Obed ahingin ahi.
\v 38 Obed hin Jehu ahingin, chule Jehu hin Azariah ahinge.
\v 39 Helez hingpa chu Azariah ahin, chule Eleasah hingpa chu Helez ahi.
\v 40 Sismai hingpa chu Eleasah ahin, chule Shallum hingpa chu Sismai ahi.
\v 41 Jekamiah hingpa chu Shallum ahin, chule Elishama hingpa chu Jekamiah ahi.
\v 42 Jerahmeel sopipa Caleb chapa te lah a apeng masapen Mesha chun Ziph ahingin, chule Mareshah hin Hebron ahinge.
\v 43 Hebron chapa te chu Korah, Tappuah, Rekem, chule Shema ahiuve.
\v 44 Shema hin Raham ahingin, Raham hin Jorkeam ahinge. Chule Rekem hin Shammai anahingin ahi.
\v 45 Shammai chapa chu Maon ahin, chule Maon chun Beth Zur ahingin ahi.
\v 46 Caleb thaikemnu chun Haran, Moza, chule Gazez ahinge; chule hichea hin Haran hin Gazez chu ahingin ahi.
\v 47 Jahdai chapa te chu Regem, Jotham, Geshan, Pelet, Ephah, chule Shaaph ahiuvin ahi.
\v 48 Caleb thaikemnu achom khat Maachah kitinu jong chun Sheber le Tirhanah ahingin ahi.
\v 49 Amanu ma ma hin jong Madmannah pa Shaaph chule Macbenah le Gibea pa Sheva anahingin ahi. Caleb hin jong chanu khat aneiyin amin Achsah akiti.
\v 50 Mihem hijat hi abonchauva Caleb son achilhah jeng ahiuve.
\p Caleb jinu Ephrathah chapa masapen Hur chapa te chu Kiriath-Jearim pa Shobal,
\p 
\v 51 Bethlehem pa Salma, chule Beth-Gader pa Hareph ahiuve.
\v 52 Kiriath-Jearim pa Shobal son achilhahho chu Haroeh sung kon Manahath mi akeh khat jen toh,
\v 53 Chule Kiriath-Jearim insung mite Ithir miho ahiuvin, Puth miho ahiuvin, Sumath miho ahiuvin, chule Mishrai miho toh ahiuve; amahoa konna hi Zorah miho le Eshtaol miho hung kondoh ahiuvin ahi.
\v 54 Salma chapa te chu Bethlehem miho ahiuvin, Netophath miho ahiuvin , Atroth-Beth-Joab miho ahiuvin , adang miho chu Manahath miho leh Zor miho akeh khat jen jong ahiuvin ahi.
\v 55 Chule Jabez khoa cheng danthu lekha sunna pang miho insung mite jong Tirath miho ahiuvin, Shimeath miho hi Recab insung penna Hammath kitipa sung peng ngen ahiuvin, Ken mi jeng ahiuve.
\c 3
\s1 David Chate
\p 
\v 1 Hebron khopia achen laiya David in ahin achapa te chu hicheng hi ahiuve: achapa apeng masapen chu Ammon ahin, apenna nu chu Ahinoam akitin Jezreel kho mi ahi. Achapa ni lhinna pa chu Daniel ahin, Carmel kho numeinu Anogail toh ahinlhon ahi.
\v 2 Athum lhinna pa chu Absalom ahin, anu chu Maacah akitin, Geshur lengpa Talmai chanu ahi. Li lhinna pa chu Adonijah ahin, anu chu Haggith ahi.
\v 3 Nga lhinna pa chu Shephatiah akitin, anu chu Abital ahi. Gup lhinna pa chu Ithream ahin, David in ajinu Eglah toh ahinlhon ahiye.
\v 4 Hebron khopia kum sagi le akeh khat sunga lengvaipoa anapan sungin David chun chapa gu hi anahingin ahi. Chujouvin kum som thumle kum thum sungin Jerusalem khopia lengvaipon anapangin ahi. \x + \xo 3:4 \xt 2 Samuel 5:4,5; 1 Lgt 2:11; 1 Thusimbu 29:27\x*
\v 5 Jerusalem khopia achen laiya David in anahin achapa te chu Shammua, Shobad, Nathan, chule Solomon ahiuve. Amaho penna nu chu Ammiel chanu Bathsheba ahi. \x + \xo 3:5 \xt 2 Samuel 11:3\x*
\v 6 Chujouvin David in chapa ko ahinbe’in amaho chu Ibhar, Elishua, Elpelet,
\v 7 Nogah, Nepheg, Japhia,
\v 8 Elishama, Eliada chule Eliphelet ahiuve.
\v 9 Athaikemho toh ahindoh ho tailouvin hichengse hi David chapa te jeng ahiuve. Ama hon sopi numei Tamar kitinu bouseh aneiyin ahi.
\v 10 Solomon son achilhah ho chu Rehoboam, Abijah, Asa, Jehoshaphat,
\v 11 Jeroram, Ahaziah, Joash,
\v 12 Amaziah,Uzziah, Jotham,
\v 13 Ahaz, Hezekiah, Manasseh,
\v 14 Amon, chule Josiah ahiuvin ahi.
\v 15 Josiah chapa te chu apeng nasapen pa Johanan ahin, ni lhinna pa Jehoiakim ahin, athum channa pa Zedekiah ahin, li lhinna pa chu Shallum ahi.
\v 16 Jehoiakim son achilhah ho chu achapa Jehoiachin leh asopipa Zedekiah ahi lhon'e.
\v 17 Babylon miten soh-chaga anakaimangu Jehoiachin chapa te chu Shealtiel,
\v 18 Malkiram, Pedaiah, Shenazzar, Jekamiah, hoshama, chule Nedabiah ahiuvin ahi.
\v 19 Pedaiah chapa te ni chu Zerubbabel le Shimei ahi lhon'e. Zerubbabel chapa te ni chu Meshullam le Hananiah ahilhonin, Amani sopinu chu Shelomith akiti.
\v 20 Aman chapa adang nga jong ahingin, amaho chu Hashubah, Ohel, Berekiah, Hasadiah, chule Jushab-Hesed ahiuve.
\v 21 Hananiah chapa te ni chu Pelatiah le Jeshaiah ahi lhon'e. Jeshaiah chapa Rephaiah ahin, Rephaiah chapa Arnan ahin, Arnan chapa Obadiah ahin, Obadiah chapa Shecaniah ahi.
\v 22 Shecaniah chapa le atute chu achapa Shemaiah ahin; chule Shemaiah chapa te chu Hattush ahin, Igal ahin, Bariah ahin, Neariah ahin, chule Shaphat pumin mi gup alhing uve.
\v 23 Neariah chapa te chu Elioenai ahin, Hizkiah ahin, chule Azrikam pumin mi thum ahiuve.
\v 24 Elioenai chapa te chu Hodaviah ahin, Eliashib ahin, Pelaiah ahin, Akkub ahin, Johanan ahin, Delaiah ahin, chule Anani ahin, abonchauvin mi sagi alhing uve.
\c 4
\s1 Judah Chate
\p 
\v 1 Judah chapa te chu Perez, Hezron, Carmi, Hur, chule Shobal ahiuve.
\v 2 Shobal chapa Reaiah kitipa hin Jahath ahingin, jahath hin Ahumai le Lahad ahingin ahi. Hichengse hi Zorath insung mite jeng ahiuvin ahi.
\v 3 Atam chapa te chu Jezreel, Ishma, Idbash, chule asopinu Hazzelelponi, Gedor hingpa,
\v 4 Penuel, chule Hushah hingpa Ezer ahiuve. Mi hicheng hi Bethlehem hingpa Ephrathah chapa apeng masapen Hur son achilhah ho ahiuvin ahi.
\v 5 Tekoa pa Ashur chun ji ni aneiyin Amani chu Helah le Naarah ahi lhon'e.
\v 6 Naarah hin Ahuzzam, Hepher, Temeni, chule Haahashtari ahingin ahi.
\v 7 Helah chun Zereth, Izhar, Ethnan,
\v 8 Chule Anub pa Koz, Zobedah le Harum chapa Aharshel insung mite chengse chu ahingin ahi.
\v 9 Jebez kitipa ji asopite dang dang sanga agunchu jeh’in anun jong, ama hi nat chungnunga kahin ahi tin amin Jabez asah’in ahi.
\v 10 Jabez hi Israel Pathen henga ataovin hiti aseiye, “O Pathen, nangin keima phathei neiboh tei teiyin lang, neikaile jing jengin lang, chule hahsatna le gentheina jousea kon’in neichom khen jing jengin,” atin ahi.
\p Hichun hiche ataona hi Pathen’in anop peh tai.
\p 
\v 11 Shuhah sopipa Kelub chun Mehir anahingin, Mehir chun Eshton ahingin,
\v 12 Eshton chun Bethrapha, Paseah, chule Tehinnah ahingin ahi. Tehinnah chun Irnahash ahingin ahi. mihem hichengse hi Recah son achilhah ahiuve.
\v 13 Kenaz chapa te ni chu Othniel le Seraiah ahilhonin ahi. Othniel chapa te ni chu Hathath le Meonothai ahi lhon'e.
\v 14 Meonothai chun Ophrah ahingin, chule Seraiah chun Geharashim pa Joab ahingin ahi; amaho hi khut them thing thembol mi ahiuve.
\v 15 Jephunneh chapa Caleb chapa te chu Iru le Elah toh Naam ahiuve; chutengleh Elah chapa chu Kenaz ahi.
\v 16 Jehallelel chapa te chu Ziph, Ziphah, Tiria, chule Asarel ahiuvin ahi.
\v 17 Ezreah chapa te chu Jether, Mered, Epher, chule Jalon ahiuvin. Mereh jinu ho lah a mi khat’in Meriam le Shammai toh Eshtemoa pa Ishba ahinpeh-in ahi.
\v 18 Chujongleh Mered hin Judah numei khat jong akichenpi’in, amanun Gedor pa Jered ahingin, Soco pa Heber ahingin, chule Zanoah pa Jekuthiel jong anahingin ahi. Mered chun Pharaoh channu Bithia kitinu jong ana kichenpi’in, chule amanun jong chapa phabep ahinpeh-in ahi.
\v 19 Hodiah jinu chu Naham sopinu anahi. Amanu chapa lah a khat chu keilah kho’a Garm mite pa ahin, chule khat pa chu Eshtomoa mi Maacath miho pa ahi.
\v 20 Shimon chapa te chu Amnon le Rinnah toh, Ben-hanan le Tilon ahiuve.
\p Ishi chapte ni chu Zoheth le Ben-Zoheth ahi lhon'e.
\p 
\v 21 Shelah kitipa hi Judah chapa te ho lah a mi khat anahi.
\p Shelah son achilhah ho chu Lecah pa Er; Mareshah pa Laasah; chule Beth-Ashbea kho’a tupatpon khonga pang insung mite toh;
\p 
\v 22 Jokim; Cozeba mite le Joash chule Jashubi-Lehem le Moab gamsunga vaipoa anapang Sraph ahiuvin ahi. mi hijat le abonchauva amin nu chu khanglui laipeh’a athusim mu kisutna lekhahoa ana kisunlut peh ahitai.
\v 23 Amaho chengse hi bel denga pang ho, Netaim le Gederah kho’a cheng ahiuve. Hichea hi amaho hi cheng khom’uva lengpa natonga pang ji ahiuve.
\v 24 Simeon chapa te chu Jemuel*, Jamin, Jarib, Zohar,* chule Shaul ahiuve.
\v 25 Shaul son achilhah ho chu Shallum le Mibsam, chule Mishma toh ahiuve.
\v 26 Mishma son achilhah ho chu achapa Hammuel ahin; Hammuel chapa Zaccur ahin; chule Zaccur chapa Shimei ahi.
\v 27 Shimei hin chapa som le gup jen ahingin, chule chanu gup ahinge; ahinlah asopi pasal dang vang cha tamnei aum pouvin ahi. Hijeh chun, Simeon insung mite hi Judah insung mite bangin apung thei mong mong pouve.
\v 28 Amaho hi Beersheba le moladah, Hazar-Shaul, \x + \xo 4:28 \xt Joshua 19:2-8\x*
\v 29 Bilhah le Ezem Tolad dunga achenguvin,
\v 30 Bethuel, Hormah, Ziklag,
\v 31 Beth-Marcoboth, Hazarsusim, Beth-biri, chule Shaaraim dunga jong acheng uve.
\v 32 David lengvaipoa ahung pan masanga kho hijat hi amaho thuneina noiya um ngen ahiuve.
\p Amaho son achilhah ho chu Etam, Ain, Rimmon, Token, chule Ashan pumin khopi nga,
\p 
\v 33 Chule kimvel dunga akhobah chengse chutoh Baalath mun chan geiyin jong achenguvin ahi. Hicheng hi amaho chenna mun ahin, chuleh, hiche min chengse ho hi amaho khanggui kisimna lekhabua ana kisun lut’ah ahi.
\v 34 Simeon son achilhah dang ho chu Meshobab, Jamlech, chule Amaziah chapa Joshah,
\v 35 Joel le Joshibiah chapa Jehu toh, Seraiah chapa ahin, Asiel chapa ahin,
\v 36 Elioenai ahin, Jaakobah ahin, Jeshohaiah ahin, Asaiah ahin, Adiel ahin, Jesimiel ahin, Benaiah ahin,
\v 37 Chule Shiphi chapa Ziza ahin, Allon chapa ahin, Jedaiah chapa ahin, Shimri chapa ahin, chule Shemaiah chapa ahi.
\v 38 Tua amin cheh’a kisimdoh ho hi Simeon insunga ama ama kailhah cheh’a haosa chapa te cheh ahiuvin; apu apau insung dungjui cheh in jong nasatah in aphatheiyuvin akhangtou theilheh jenguve.
\v 39 Chule amaho hi Gerar gamkai langa akitol’uvin, phaicham gam'a niso lam geiyin jong acheuvin, akelngoi hon teu din hamhing um umna ahol’uvin ahi.
\v 40 Hikom'a chun ama hon gam phatah, hamhing thalhinna gam len tah, chule chamlenna le lung mong tah’a chenna thei akimuve.
\p Hiche gam a ana cheng masa mite chu Ham son achilhah mi phabep anahiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 41 Hinlah, Simeon insunga ama ama kailhah cheh’a haosa chapa te chu hikom'a hin Judah lengpa Hezekiah lengvaipoh layin ahung lut’uvin, hikom'a anachengte Ham son achilhah phabep ho chule Meun mite ponbuh ho ahin, achennau in ho ahin, amuphah phah asumanguvin ahi. Hiti hin amaho chu asuhmang phat’uvin amaho khel’in anachenguvin, tuni gei hin ama hon mun chu alo nalaiyuve. Ijeh-inem itileh hiche gam'a hi akelngoiteu neh ding hamhing pha amu’u ahi.
\v 42 Chuin, Simeon mite lah a mihem ja nga tobang chu Seir molsang geiyin akitol’uvin, a lamkai diuvin Pelatiah le Neariah toh, Rephaiah, le Uzziel, abonchauva Ishi chapa te chu anapansah uvin ahi.
\v 43 Amaho hin Amalek mi athimoh’a jamdoh chengse jong asumanguvin, chule amaho khel’in tuni geiyin acheng den tauve.
\c 5
\s1 Reuben Chate
\p 
\v 1 Israel cha amasapen chu Reuben ahi. Ahinlah, aman apa jalou tah’a apa thaikemho lah a khat alupkhom-pi jeh chun a upat hi asopipa Joseph chapa te joh achanguvin. Hiche jeh a chu Reuben hi khanggui kisimna lekhabua chun apen masah dungjuijin akijih lut tapoi. \x + \xo 5:1 \xt Semtilbu 35:22; 49:3,4\x*
\v 2 Judah son achilhah te chu athahat pen’a ahung pan uva chule amaho phunga konna leng khat ahung kisep doh jing vang'in, upatna kiti hi Joseph bou achangin ahi. \x + \xo 5:2 \xt Semtilbu 49:8-10\x*
\v 3 Israel chapa apeng masapen Reuben chapa te chu Hanoch ahin, Pallu ahin, Hezron ahin, chule Carmi ahi.
\v 4 Joel son achilhah ho chu Shemaiah ahin, Gog ahin, Shimei ahin, \x + \xo 5:4 \xt 2 Lengte 15:29\x*
\v 5 Micah ahin, Reaiah ahin, Baal ahin,
\v 6 Chule Beerah ahi. Assyria lengpa Tiglath-Pileser pa chu Beerah anahi.
\v 7 Beerah inkote chu ama phung sunga akhangguiya akisimtoh’a akijih toh tengleh ahaosa chu Jeriel ahin, Zechariah jong ahi;
\v 8 Chule Azaz chapa Bela ahin, Shema chapa ahin, chule Joel chapa jong ahi. Reuben mite ho hi Aroer apat Nebon chan gei, chule Baal-Meon chan geiya cheng ahiuve.
\v 9 Chule amaho hin Gilead gam'a chun gancha tamtah anei jeh a niso lama jong achenguvin, nel gam jot nalampi lang apat Euphrates luipi gal lam geiyin acheng uvin ahi.
\v 10 Shual lengvaipoh laiyin jong Reuben mite hin Hagar mite chunga gal abol uvin ahi, hiche Hagar mite chu ajophat uvin Gilead niso lama amaho ponbuh jouse a chun alhung keiyin achen den lo tauvin ahi.
\v 11 Gad son achilhah ho chu Reuben mite ho toh kigalsaiyin achenguvin Salecah chan geiyin alouve.
\v 12 Joel chu Bashan khoa haosan apangin, Shapham ama ban in apangin, ama ni ban’a Janai le Saphat apang ahi lhon'e.
\v 13 Amaho insunga phunggui sagi haosa ho chu Michael ahin, Meshullam ahin, Shiba ahin, Jorai ahin, Jacan Zia ahin, chule Eber ahi.
\v 14 Hiche ho chengse hi abonchauva Huri chapa Abihail son achilhah jeng ahiuve; Huri chu joroah chapa ahin, Joroah chu Gilead chapa ahin, Michael chu Jeshishai chapa ahin, Jeshishai chu Jahdo chapa, chule Jahdo chu Buz chapa ahi.
\v 15 Ahi chu Abdiel chapa ahin, Abdiel chu Guni chapa ahin chule Guni hi amaho insung lhah’a haosa ahi.
\v 16 Hiche Gad mite hi Gilead gamsung, Bashan gamsung, chule akhobah jouse le Sharon gam hamhing phatna lai jousea achenguvin ahi.
\v 17 Mihem hijat khanggui thusim hi Judah lengpa Jotham lal lai le Israel lengpa Jeroboam lal laiya kisimtoh a kijih doh ahiye.
\v 18 Reuben chapa te leh Gad chapa te chule Manaseh phung keh khat jong hin galhang mihat, pho le chemjam thoa gal bolthei, thalpi kap them, galsat themtah tah sepai sangsom li le sang ni le ja sagi le somgup jen gal bol dia gonsa anei jing uvin ahi.
\v 19 Amaho hin Hagar mite chung le Jetur mite chung, chule Naphish mite le Nodab mite chunga gal abol’uve.
\v 20 Gal lai hin ama hon Pathen hengah panpina athum un, ama hon Pathen tahsanna anei jeh’uvin, aman ataona chu asanpeh tai. Hijeh chun ama hon Gar mite le amaho panpi chengse chu ajou soh hel tauve.
\v 21 ama hon akisatpi Har mite thil achompeh ho chu sangongsao sangsom nga jen ahin, kelngoi le kelcha sang jani le sangsom nga jen toh ahin, chule mihem sang jakhat jen galhingin akaiyun ahi.
\v 22 Gal kisat chu Pathen'in apanpi jeh’in Har mite simsen lou akijam chap jengin ahi. Soh-changa akitol mang kah seuvin amaho gamsunga chun Reuben mite, Gad mite, chu Manaseh mite acheng tauve.
\v 23 Manaseh phung kehkhat jong mihem atam lheh jenguvin, Bashan gam'a pat Baal-Hermon gei, Senir gei, chule Hermon molsang geiyin achengdoh peh jenguvin ahi.
\v 24 Ama ama pajang lhah a insung cheh-uva a upa chengse chu: Epher ahin, Ishi ahin, Eliel ahin, Azriel ahin, Jeremiah ahin, Hodaviah ahin, chule Jahdiel toh ahiuve. Amaho mihat galhang ho hina lama minthanna anei uvin, chule ama ama insung pajang lhah a a upa chengse chu ahitauvin ahi.
\v 25 Ahivangin amaho hin apu apateu Pathen ahou khel’uvin, Pathen'in asuhmangsa mite gam'a vaipo ho Pathen limsemthu doi ho akou tauvin ahi.
\v 26 Hiche jeh hin Pathen'in Assyria lengpa Pul (Tiglath-Piteser jong akiti ) lungthim ahintildoh peh in, hiche Reuben mite le Gad mite toh, chule Manaseh phung akeh khat hi akaimangin ahi. Assyria ten amaho hi Halah kho le Habor kho, Hara kho, chule Gozan vadunga ahinkai lut’uvin, tuni geiyin aumden tauve. \x + \xo 5:26 \xt 2 Lengte 15:19; \xt 2 Lengte 15:29; \xt 2 Lengte 17:6\x*
\c 6
\s1 Levi Chate
\p 
\v 1 Levi chapa te chu Gershon ahin, Kohath ahin, chule Merari toh ahiuve.
\v 2 Kohath son achilhah ho chu Amram ahin, Izhar ahin, Hebron ahin, chule Uzziel toh ahiuve.
\v 3 Amram chapa te chu Aaron ahin, Moses ahin, chule Miriam toh ahi. Aaron chapa te chu Nadab, Abihu, Eleazar, chule Ithamar toh hichengse hi ahiuve.
\v 4 Eleazer hin Phinehas anahingin, Phinehas hin Abishua anahinge.
\v 5 Abishua hin Bukki anahingin, Bukki hin Uzzi ahinge.
\v 6 Uzzi hin Zerahiah ahingin, Zerahiah in Meraioth ahinge.
\v 7 Meraioth hin Amariah ahingin, Amariah hin Ahitub ahinge.
\v 8 Ahitub hin Zadok ahingin, Zadok hin Ahimaaz ahinge.
\v 9 Johanan hin Azariah chu ahingin, Azariah chun Johanan ahinge.
\v 10 Johanan hin Azariah chu ahingin, ama hi Jerusalem khopia Solomon Hou-In sahdoh sunga Thempu Chungnunga hung pang ahi.
\v 11 Azariah hin Amariah ahingin, Amariah chun Ahitub ahinge.
\v 12 Ahitub hin Zadok ahingin, Zadok chun Shallum ahinge.
\v 13 Shallum hin Hilkiah ahingin, Hilkiah chun Azariah ahinge.
\v 14 Azariah hin Seraiah ahingin, Seraiah chun Jehozadak ahingin ahi.
\v 15 Pakaiyin Judah mite leh Jerusalem mite soh-changa asol manga Nebuchadnezzar khut’a atolmang sah phat’in Jehozadak jong hi soh-changin achemang tan ahi.
\v 16 Levi chapa te chu Gershon ahin, Kohath ahin, chule Merari ahi. \x + \xo 6:16 \xt Potdohbu 6:16-19\x*
\v 17 Gershom chapa te ni chu Libni leh Shimei ahi lhon'e.
\v 18 Kohath son achilhah ho chu Amram ahin, Izhar ahin, Hebron ahin, chule Uzziel ahi.
\v 19 Merari son achilhah teni chu Mahli le Mushi ahi lhon'e.
\p Anoiya mi hichengse hi apu apau kailhah cheh ama ama insung dol cheh’a Levi miho insung jeng ahiuve:
\p 
\v 20 Gershon insung ahileh, Libni ahin, Jahath ahin, Zimmah ahin,
\v 21 Joah ahin, Iddo ahin, Zerah ahin, chule Jeatherai ahi.
\v 22 Kohath son achilhah ho chu Amminadab ahin, Korah ahin, Assir ahin,
\v 23 Elkanah ahin, Abiasaph ahin, ahimoth ahin,
\v 24 Tahath ahin, Uriel ahin, Uzziah ahin, chule Shaul ahi.
\v 25 Elkanah son chilhah ho ahileh, Amasai ahin, Ahimoth ahin,
\v 26 Elkanah ahin, Zophai ahin, Nahath ahin,
\v 27 Eliah ahin, Jehoram ahin, Elkanah ahin, chule Samuel ahi.
\v 28 Samuel chapa te ni chu apeng masa Joel ahin, chule anni lhinna pa chu Abijah ahi.
\v 29 Merari son achilhah ho chu Mahli ahin, Libni ahin, Shimei ahin, Uzzah ahin,
\v 30 Shimei ahin, Haggiah ahin, chule Asaiah ahi.
\v 31 Pakai Hou-In sunga Pathen thingkong ahung kitol lut nunga David’in Hou-In sunga la lamkaiya pang dia anganse miho chu hicheng hi ahiuve.
\v 32 Jerusalem khopia Solomonin Pakai Hou-In asah doh masangsen la lamkaiya pang ho hi mipi kikhopna ponbuh’a la lamkaiyin anapanguvin lhacha na atong jing uve. Hitobang hin ama hon atoh dingdol kinse chu hoikeichan atong jing jenguve.
\v 33 Hichea la lamkaiya pang ho leh achapa teu chu aban'a kisei ho hi ahi-uve:
\p Heman tumging thempa chu Kohath chilhah miho lah a Joel chapa ahin, Joel chu Samuel chapa ahin,
\p 
\v 34 Samuel chu Elkanah chapa ahin, Elkanah chu Jeroham chapa ahin, Jeroham chu Eliel chapa ahin, Eliel chu Toah chapa ahin,
\v 35 Toah chu Zuph chapa ahin, Zuph chu Elkanah chapa ahin, Elkanah chu Mahath chapa ahin, Mahath chu Amasai chapa ahi.
\v 36 Amasai chu Elkanah chapa ahin, Elkanah chu Joel chapa ahi, Joel chu Azariah chapa ahin, Azariah chu Zephaniah chapa ahi.
\v 37 Zephaniah chu Tahath chapa ahin, Tahath chu Assir chapa ahin, Assir chu Ebiasaph chapa ahin, Ebiasaph chu Korah chapa ahi.
\v 38 Korah chu Izhar chapa ahin, Izhar chu Kohath chapa ahi; Kohath chu Levi chapa ahin, Levi chu Israel chapa ahi.
\v 39 Heman’in manchah phapenna anei masapa Gershon chilhah miho lah a Asaph kitipa chu Berekiah chapa ahin, Berekiah chu Shimea chapa ahi;
\v 40 Shimea hi Michael chapa ahin, Michael chu Baaseiah chapa ahi. Baaseiah chu Malkijah chapa ahin,
\v 41 Malkijah chu Ethnic chapa ahi; Ethnic chu Zerah chapa ahin, Zerah chu Adaiah chapa ahi,
\v 42 Adaiah chu Ethan chapa ahin, Ethan chu Zimmah chapa ahi; Zimmah chu Shimei chapa ahin,
\v 43 Shimei chu Jathah chapa ahi; Jathah chu Gershom chapa ahin, Gershom chu Levi chapa ahi.
\v 44 Hemanin manchah phapenna anei ani channa pa Merari chilhah miho lah a Ethan chu Kishi chapa ahin, Kishi chu Abdi chapa ahin, Abdi chu Malluch chapa ahin,
\v 45 Malluch chu Hashabiah chapa ahin, Hashabiah chu Amaziah chapa ahin, Amaziah chu Hilkiah chapa ahin,
\v 46 Hilkiah chu Amzi chapa ahin, Amzi chu Bani chapa ahin, Bani chu Shemer chapa ahin,
\v 47 Shemer chu Mahli chapa ahin, Mahli chu Mushi chapa ahin, Mushi chu Merari chapa ahin chule Merari chu Levi chapa ahiye.
\v 48 Amaho sopite Levi phung sung mite jouse chu abonchauvin Pathen Hou-In Houbuh sunga natong kinbol din akipansah sohkeiyuvin ahi.
\v 49 Aaron le achapa te jeng bouseh chu Thempu kin tongin apanguvin ahi. Ama hon pumgo thilto kigona maicham chung le gimnaitwi kihalvamna maicham chunga thilto ding jouse toh-soh in apanguvin, Muntheng Phunga natohna ding thil toh din apanguve, chujongleh Pathen lhachapa Mose thupeh dungyuiyin Israel te kithoina kinbol’in apang jiuve.
\v 50 Aaron son chilhah ho chu hicheng hi ahiuve: Aaron chapa chu Eleazar ahin, Eleazar chapa chu Phinehas ahin, Phinehas chapa chu Abishua ahi.
\v 51 Abishua chapa chu Bukki ahin, Bukki chapa chu Uzzi ahin, Uzzi chapa chu Zerahiah ahi.
\v 52 Zerahiah chapa chu Meraioth ahin, Meraioth chapa chu Amariah ahin; Amariah chapa chu Ahitub ahi.
\v 53 Ahitub chapa chu Zadok ahin, chule Zadok chapa chu Ahimaaz ahiye.
\v 54 Hichengse hi amaho gamgi hop sunga achenna mun chengseu chu ahiye: Aaron chapa te Kohath phung sung mite dinga phun kisan chu aphat jeh’in,
\v 55 Mihon amaho chu Judah gamsunga Hebron khopi le akimvel gamse se toh chule avel’a hamhing gam gancha vahna ding jouse chutoh apeh tha taove;
\v 56 Amavang akhopi loujao lah chengse leh akhoneo dung jouse chu Caleb kitipa Jephunneh chapa chu apetauve.
\v 57 Aaron chapa dinga khopi anapeh’u chule ahamhing gamsunga cheh toh anakipeh tha ho chu: Hebron khopi ( kiselna khopi ), Libnah khopi, Jattir khopi, Eshtemoa khopi,
\v 58 Holon khopi, Debir khopi,
\v 59 Ain khoppi, Juttah khopi, chule Beth-Shemesh khopi toh hichengse hi ahi.
\v 60 Chuleh Benjamin phunga konna alahdoh-u khopi ho chu Gibeon khopi le ahamhing gamsungse toh ahin, Geba khopi le ahamhing gamsungse toh ahin, Alemeth khopi le ahamhing gamsungse toh ahin,chule Anatholh khopi le ahamhing gamsungse toh ahi. Aaron chapa te a insung pumpiuva achan jat’u khopi chu abonchan khopi som le khopi thum alhingin ahi.
\v 61 Kohath chapa te amoh chengse din Bamau insung dinga phum aphatna dungjuijin, Manasseh phung keh khat, hichea phunga kon chun khopi som khat jen akipen ahi.
\v 62 Gershom chapa te chu phun kisan aphat dungjuijin, Issachar gam'a kon, Asher gam'a kon, Naphtali gam'a kon, chule Jordan solam’a um Bashan gam'a Manasseh phunga konna kidong khom khopi agomin khopi som le khopi thum achanguvin ahi.
\v 63 Merari chapa te jong phun kisan aphat dungjuijin, Reuben gam'a kon, Gad gam'a kon, chule Zebulun gam'a kon kidong khom khopi som le khopi ni acheng uvin ahiye.
\v 64 Hitobang hin Israel chaten Levi te chu khopi chujat chutoh ahamhing gamsese toh anapeuvin ahiye.
\v 65 Hitobang hin phun phatna dungjuijin, Judah phunga kon, Simeon phunga kon, chule Benjamin phunga kon'in achunga kisei khopi ho hi anapeuvin ahi.
\v 66 Kohath chapa te insung mi phabep jong Ephraim phunga kon'in agamsung uva khopi phabep le ahamhing gamsungse cheh achanguvin,
\v 67 hiche khopi ho chu: Shechem ( kiselna hoidohna khopi Ephraim thinglhang gam'a um ) ahin, Gezer khopi ahin,
\v 68 Jokmeam khopi ahin, Beth-horon khopi ahin,
\v 69 Aijalon khopi ahin, chule Gath-Rimmon khopi chengse hi ahi.
\v 70 Kohath chapa te amoh chengse kipe khopi ho chu Manasseh phung keh khat’a kon'in jong Aner le bileam khopi cheh leh Ahamhing gamsungse cheh toh ahin ahi.
\v 71 Gershon insung mite kipe khopi ho chu Bashan gamsunga Golan khopi le ahamhing gamsungsese, chule Manasseh phung keh khat’a konna Ashtaroth khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahiye.
\v 72 Isssachar phunga konna kipedoh khopi ho chu Kedesh khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin, Deberath khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se,
\v 73 Ramoth khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se le Anem khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahi.
\v 74 Asher phunga konna kipedoh khopi ho chu Mashal khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se, Abdon khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se,
\v 75 Hakok khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se, chule Rehob khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahi.
\v 76 Naphtali phung sunga konna kipedoh khopi ho chu, Galilee gamsunga Kedesh khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin, Hammon khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se, chule Kiriathaim khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahi.
\v 77 Merari chate amoh chengse chu Zebulun phunga kon'in Jokneam khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin, Kartah khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin, Rimmon khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin, chule Tabor khopi ahamhing gamsungse se akipen ahi.
\v 78 Reuben phung sunga konna kipe khopi ho chu Jordan vadung gal lang Jericho khopi dunga, Jordan kal niso lam’a Bezer khopi ( Nel khopi ) le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin, Jahaz khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin,
\v 79 Kedermoth khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin, chule Mephaath khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se toh akipen ahi.
\v 80 Chutengleh Gad phunga konna kipedoh khopi ho chu Gilead gamsunga Ramoth khopi le ahamhing gamsungsese ahin,
\v 81 Heshbon khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se ahin, chule Jazer khopi le ahamhing gamsungsese ahi.
\c 7
\s1 Issachar Chate
\p 
\v 1 Issachar chapa li ho chu Tol'a, Puah, Jashub, chule Shimron ahiuve.
\v 2 Tol'a chapa te chu Uzzi le Rephaiah toh, Jeriel le Jahmai toh, Ibsam le Shemuel ahiuve. Amaho hi apau Tol'a insungkon mite lah a upa cheh ahiuve. Daniel lal laiyin amaho hi gal-hang mihat jeng ahiuvin, sepai 22,600 alhinguvin ahi.
\v 3 Uzzi chapa chu Izrahiah ahi. Izrahiah chapa te chu Michael, Obadiah, Joel, chule Isshiah ahiuve. Amaho mi nga hi aphung sung uva lamkai cheh in apanguve.
\v 4 Amaho hi numei ji tampi le chapa tamtah aneiyuvin, hijeh chun amaho chapa te sunga galsat thei sepai hi agomin mi 36,000 alhinguve.
\v 5 Issachar insung mite mong mong jong gal-hang mihat jeng jeng jong abonchauvin 87,000 alhinguvin ahi. Amaho cheng chu akhanggui lekhabu’va kijih lut’ah ahitai.
\v 6 Benjamin chapa thum ho chu Bela, Beker chule Jediael ahiuve.
\v 7 Bela chapa nga ho chu Ezbon le Uzzi toh, Uzziel le Jerimoth toh, chule Iri ahiuvin ahi. Amaho hi amau insung apu apau lhah’a phung upa cheh ahiuve. Chujongleh akhangguiyu kisimna akisut dol chun gal-hang sepai agomin 22,034 alhinguve.
\v 8 Beker chapa te chu Zemirah ahin, Joash ahin, Eliezer ahin, Elioenai ahin, Omri ahin, Jeremoth ahin, Abijah ahin, Anathoth ahin, chule Alemeth toh ahiuve.
\v 9 Amaho hi apu apateu lhah’a insung upa cheh ahiuve. Amaho hi akhangguiya lekhabu’a kisut lut dungjuijin mihat gal-hang sese le lamkai sese chu agomin mihem 20,200 alhinguvin ahi.
\v 10 Jediael chapa chu Bilhan ahi. Bilhan chapa te chu Jeush le Benjamin toh, Ehud le Kenaanah toh, Zethan le Tarshish toh chule Ahishahar ahiuve.
\v 11 Amaho cheng hi apu apateu insunga phung upa cheh ahiuve. Hichengse phung sunga hin gal-hang mihat galbol thei cheh agomin 17,200 alhinguve.
\v 12 Ir chapa te ni chu Shuppim le Huppim ahi lhon'e. Hushim chu apa Aker ahi.
\v 13 Naphtali chapa te chu Jahzeel ahin, Guni ahin, Jezer ahin, chule Shillem ahiuve. Amaho chengse hi Jacob thaikemnu son achilhah jeng ahiuve.
\v 14 Manasseh son achilhah ho lah a Aramean numeinu toh ahin chu Asriel ahi. Amanu hin Gilead hingpa Makir jong ahinge.
\v 15 Makir hin Huppim le Shuppim jong ji apuipeh cheh’e. Makir hin sopi numei khat aneiyin amin Macaah akiti. Ason chilhah ho lah a numei khat chu Zelophehad ahin, amanu hin chanu jeng bou ahingin ahi.
\v 16 Makir jinu Macaah chun chapa khat ahingin amin jong Peresh asah’e ; chule asopipa min chu Sheresh ahi. Peresh chapa te ni chu Ulam le Rakem ahi lhon'e.
\v 17 Ulam chapa chu Bedan ahi. Hichengse hi Manasseh chapa Makir son chilhah ho lah a Gilead insung mite jeng ahiuve.
\v 18 Makir sopinu Hammoleketh kitinu chun Ishod, Abiezer, chule Mahlah ahingin ahi.
\v 19 Shemida chapa te chu Ahian, Shechen, Likhi, chu Aniam ahiuvin ahi.
\v 20 Ephraim son chilhah ho chu Shuthelah ahin, Bered ahin, Tahath ahin, Eleadah ahin, Tahath ahikit’in,
\v 21 Zabad ahin, Shuthelah akiti kit’in, Ezer ahin, Elead ahiye. Ezer le Elead,, ama ni hi Gath kimvella cheng loulhou mi hon anathat tauvin ahi: ijeh-inem itileh ama ni hi aganchau guhpeh dinga hung konsuh jing ahi lhon'e.
\v 22 Apau Ephraim chun nikho phabep sungin amaho pul adou jengin, alhem lung mong din asopite jong ahung uvin ahi.
\v 23 Chujouvin Ephraim hin ajinu aluppi kit’in ahileh amanu ahung gaiyin chapa khat ahing kit’e: a insunga chutobang vangsetna alhun jeh’in Ephraim in achapa pengthahpa chu Beriah akisah’in ahi.
\v 24 Aman chanu khat ahingin amin jong Sheerah akitin ahi. Amanu hin Beth-horon chungnung le anoinung chu anasadoh’in chule Uzzer-Sheerah jong anasadoh’e.
\v 25 Ephraim son chilhah ho chu Rephah ahi, Resheph ahin, Telah ahin, Tahan ahin,
\v 26 Ladan ahin, Ammihud ahin, Elishama ahin,
\v 27 Nun ahin, chule Joshua ahiye.
\v 28 Ephraim son chilhah hon gam alouva achenphana mun’u chu Bethel khopi le agamsunga kho lehn dom jouse toh, niso lama Naaran ahin, nilhum lama Gezer le akho lehn dung jouse jong ahithan, chule Shechem khopi le akho lehn len ho jong ahin, Ayyah khopi le akho lehn dung jouse chan gei jong ahithai.
\v 29 Chutengleh Manasseh mite gamgi dunga hung kilhah ahipeh’in, Beth-Shan le akho lehn dung jouse ahin, Taanaeh le akho lehn ho toh, Megiddo kho leh akho lehn dung jouse le Dork ho leh le akho lehn dom jouse toh ahiye. Khopi hijat sunga hi Israel chapa Joseph son chilhah chengse anacheng ahiuve.
\v 30 Asher chapa te chu Imnah ahin, Ishvah ahin, Ishvi ahin, chule Beriah ahiuve. Ama hon sopi numei khat aneiyuvin amin Serah ahi.
\v 31 Beriah chapa te ni chu Heber le Malkiel ahilhonin, Malkiel hi Birzaith pa ahiye.
\v 32 Heber chapa te chu Japhlet le Shomer toh, chule Hotham ahiuve. Amaho hin sopi numei khat bou aneiyuvin amin Shua akiti.
\v 33 Japhlet chapa te hin Pasach, Bimhal, chule Ashvath ahiuve.
\v 34 Shomer chapa te chu Ahi, Rohgah, Hubbah, chule Ram ahiuve.
\v 35 Shomer sopipa Helem chapa te chu Zophah, Imma, Shelesh, chule Amal ahiuve.
\v 36 Zophah chapa te chu Suah, Harnephar, Shual, Beri, Imrah,
\v 37 Bezer, Hod, Shamma, Shilshah, Ithran, chule Beera ahiuve.
\v 38 Jether chapa te chu Arah le Hanniel toh, chule Rizia ahiuvin ahi.
\v 39 Ulla chapa te chu Arah le Hanniel toh, chule Rizia ahiuve.
\v 40 Asher son achilhah mi hichengse hi, apajang khai cheh’a phung upa jeng ahiuve. Mihat gal-hang mi jeng leh milen milal jeng ahiuve, ti phatea phot chetsa cheh ahi tauve. Akhanggui lekhabua galsat’a manthei cheh mihing kisimdoh chengse chu 26,000 alhinguvin ahi.
\c 8
\s1 Benjamin Chate
\p 
\v 1 Benjamin chapa apeng masapen chu Bela ahin, ni lhinna pa chu Ashbel ahin, athum channa pa chu Aharah ahin,
\v 2 Li lhinna pa chu Nohah ahin, chule a nga channapa chu Rapha ahi.
\v 3 Bela chapa te chu Addar ahin, Gera ahin, Abihud ahin,
\v 4 Abishua ahin, Naaman ahin, Ahoah ahin,
\v 5 Gera ahin, Shephuphan ahin, chule Huram ahiuve.
\v 6 Ehud chapa te,Gam'a cheng mite dinga a insung cheh uva mi upa jeng ho chu, abonchauvin Manahath gamsunga min soh-chang din akaimang tauve.
\v 7 Ehud chapa te chu Naaman ahin, Ahijah ahin, chule Gera toh ahiuve. Gera hin soh-changa apuimang’u ahin, ama hin Uzza le Abihud ahingin ahi.
\v 8 Shaharaim hin ajite ni Hushim le Baara ada nungin jong Moab gamsunga cha tampi anei nalaiyin ahi.
\v 9 Ajinu Hodesh kiti nu chuto jong chapa Jobab le Zibia toh Mesha le Malcam ahing lhonin,
\v 10 Jeuz le Sakia toh, chule Mirmah ahing lhonin ahi. Hichengse hi amapa chapa te ahiuvin, a insung cheh uva mi upa cheh ahiuve.
\v 11 Aman ajinu Hashim toh jong chapa ni Abitub leh Elpaal ahing lhonin ahi.
\v 12 Elpaal chapa te chu Eber ahin, Misham ahin, chule Shemed ahi: ( Shemed hin Ono khopi le Lod khopi toh chule akho lehn dung jouse anasan ahin),
\v 13 Beriah ahin, chule Shema jong ahi lhon'e. Amaho hi Aijalon khopi’a cheng insung phung upa cheh ahiuvin, chule Gath’a cheng ho toh kisat’a nomanga pang ho chu ahiuve.
\v 14 Chujongleh Ahio le Shashak toh chule Jeremoth jong ahiuve.
\v 15 Zebadiah ahin, Arad ahin, chule Eder jong ahiuve.
\v 16 Michael le Ishpah toh Joha, amaho hi Beriah chapa te jeng ahiuve.
\v 17 Zebadiah ahin, Izliah ahin, chule Jobab, amaho chengse hi Elpaal chapa te jeng ahiuvin ahi.
\v 18 Ishmerai ahin, Izliah ahin, chule Jobab, amaho chengse hi Elpaal chapa te jeng ahiuvin ahi.
\v 19 Jakim ahin, Zicri ahin, Zabdi ahi,
\v 20 Elienai ahin, Zillethai ahin, Eliel ahin,
\v 21 Adaiah ahin, Beriah ahin, chule Shimrath ahin, amaho hi Shimei chapa te ahiuve.
\v 22 Ishpan, Eber, Eliel,
\v 23 Abdon, Zicri, Hanan,
\v 24 Hananiah, Elam, Anthothijah,
\v 25 Iphdeiah, chule Penuel hichengse hi Shashak chapa te jeng ahiuve.
\v 26 Shamsherai, Shehariah, Athaliah,
\v 27 Jaareshiah, Elijah, chule Zicri hichengse hi Jeroham chapa te ahiuvin ahi.
\v 28 Mihem hijat hi akhangguiyu lekhabua kisut dungjuijin ama ama insunga phung upa cheh ahiuvin, chule amaho hi Jerusalem khopia anachenguvin ahiye.
\v 29 Gibeon pa Jeiel chu Gibeon khopia anachengin ahi. Ajinu min chu Maacah ahin,
\v 30 Chule achapa apeng masapen chu Abdon akitin ahi. Jeiel chapa te adang ho chu Zur, Kish, Baal, Ner, Nadab,
\v 31 Gedor, Ahio, Zechariah,
\v 32 Chule Shimeam hingpa Mikloth ahiuve. Amaho chengse hi ainkoteu toh kigalsai cheh’in Jerusalem khopia chun anachenguvin ahi.
\v 33 Ner chun Kish ahingin, Kish chun Saul ahingin, Saul’in Jonathan, Malkishua, Abinadab, chule Eshbaal ahinge.
\v 34 Jonathan’in Meribaal ahingin, Meribaal in Micah ahinge.
\v 35 Micah chapa te chu Pithon, Melech, Tahrea, chule Ahaz ahiuve.
\v 36 Ahaz chun Jadah ahingin, Jadah chun Alemeth, Azmaveth, chule Zimri ahinge. Zimri hin Moza ahinge.
\v 37 Moza chu Binea pa ahin, Binea chu Rephaiah pa ahin, Raphaiah chu Eleasah pa ahin, chule Eleasah chu Azel pa ahi.
\v 38 Azel hin chapa gup aneiyin, amaho chu: Azrikam, Bokeru, Ishmael, Sheariah, Obadiah, chule Hanan ahiuve. Amaho chengse hi Azel chapa te jeng ahiuvin ahi.
\v 39 Ezel sopipa Eshek chun chapa thum ahingin ahi: Apeng masapen chu Ulam ahin, ani lhinna pa chu Jeush ahin, chule athum channa pa chu Eliphelet ahi.
\v 40 Ulam chapa te chu mihat gal-hang jeng, thalpi kap them jeng ahiuvin ahi. Ama hon chapa tampi pi aneiyuvin chule tute jong tamtah aneiyun, abonchauvin mi 150 jen alhinguve. Mi hichengse hi Benjamin son chilhah jeng ahiuvin ahi.
\c 9
\s1 Jerusalem Mipite
\p 
\v 1 Hijeh chun Israel te chun abonchauvin akhangguiyu akisim sohkeiyin, akisim doh jouse chu Israel Lengte thusim lekhabua akijih lut sohkeiye.
\p Judah miten Pakaiya kitah louna anei jeh uvin Babylon gamsunga soh-changin min akaimang taove
\p 
\v 2 Agamsung uva hung lut kit’a akhopi dunguva hung cheng lut masaho chu thempu ho, Levi mite, Hou-In lhacha ho, chule Israel mite adang dang ahiuve. \x + \xo 9:2 \xt Ezra 2:27; Nehemiah 7:73\x*
\v 3 Judah mite lah a abang bang, Benjamin phunga ahin, Ephraim phunga ahin, chule Manasseh phunga ahiuvin, Jerusalem khopia ahung kitol lut’uvin chule achenguve.
\v 4 Judah chapa Perez chapa te lah a inko khat hung kinungle chu achapa Bani, Bani chapa Imri , Imri chapa Omri, Omri chapa Ammihud, Ammihud chapa Uthai chu ahi.
\v 5 Adang inko ahung kinungle ho chu Shilon mite lah a achapa apeng masapen Asaiah le achapa te ahiuve.
\v 6 Zerah phung sunga ahung kinungle chu Jevel le ainkote chengse ahiuve. Judah phung sunga ahung kinungle inko chu abonchauvin 690 alhinguvin ahi.
\v 7 Benjamin phung kon’in Meshullam chapa Sallu ahin, Sallu chapa Hodaviah ahin, Hodaviah chapa Hassenuah ahin,
\v 8 Jeroham chapa Ibneiah ahin, chule Elah chu Uzzi chapa Micri chapa ahin, chule Meshullam jong chu Shephatiah chapa ahin, Shephatiah chu Reuel chapa ahin, Reuel chu Ibnijah chapa ahi.
\v 9 Amaho chengse hi ama ama insung lhah’a phung upa cheh ahiuvin, chule akhanguiyu thusim lekhabua kijih lut sohkei ahiuve. Benjamin phunga konna hung kinungle agomin'inko 956 alhinguve.
\v 10 Thempuho lah a hung kinungle ho chu Jedaiah le Jehoiarib toh Jakin ahiuve.
\v 11 Azariah kitipa Hilkiah chapa jong chu ahin, Hilkiah chu Meshullam chapa ahi; Meshullam chu Zadok chapa ahin, Zadok chu Meraioth chapa ahi; Meraioth chu Ahitub chapa ahi. Azariah chu Pathen Hou-In’a vaibol lamkai pipua pang ahiye.
\v 12 Thempu adang hung kinungle ho chu Jehoram chapa Adaiah ahin, Jehoram hi Pashhur chapa ahin, Pashhur chu Malkijah chapa ahin, chule Aiel chapa Maasai ahin, Meshullam chu Meshillemith chapa ahin, chule Meshillemith chu Immer chapa ahi.
\v 13 Hicheng tilouvin jong thempu adang ahung kinungle agomin mi 1,760 ahiuve. Amaho hi apu apauva a insung kailhah’a phung upa chengse ahiuvin, chule mi hangsan ngen jong ahiuve. Chule amaho hi Pathen Hou-In sunga natonga mopohna nei cheh ahiuve.
\v 14 Levi phunga mite chu Hasshub chapa Shemaiah ahin, Hasshub chu Azrikam chapa ahi; Hazrikam chu Hashabiah chapa ahin, Hashabiah chu Merari chapa te lah a khat ahi.
\v 15 Bakbakkar, Herish leh Galal jong ahiuvin, chutengleh Mica chapa Mattaniah ahin, Mica chu Zicri c hapa ahin, Zicri chu Asaph chapa ahi.
\v 16 Chule Shemaiah chapa Obadiah ahin, Shemaiah chu Galal chapa ahi; Galal chu Jeduthun chapa ahin, chule Asa chapa Berekiah ahi; Berekiah chu Elkaneh chapa ahin, ama hi Netophah gamsunga cheng anahi.
\v 17 Kulpi kelkot ngah’a pang miho chu Shallum ahin, Akkub ahin, Talmon ahin, Ahiman ahin, chule a inkoteu toh ahiuve.
\v 18 Chule masang chun amaho hi niso lama lengpa kelkot ngah’in apanguve. Hiche miho hin Levi mite ngahmun kelkot jong angah’uvin ahi.
\v 19 Kore chapa Shallum ahin, Kore chu Ebiasaph chapa ahin; Korah phunggui akon ahi. Ama le ainkote, Korah mite chengse chu Hou-In kinbol’in apu apateu Pakai ngahmun ngah’a apan banguvin apanguve.
\v 20 Masanglaiya chu Eleazar chapa Phinehas kitipa hi amaho kulpi kelkot mopoa anapang ji ahi; hijeh chun Pakaiyin jong amapa chu ana umpi jing jenge.
\v 21 Chule hiche jou chun Zechariah kitipa Meshelemiah chapa chu kikhopna ponbuh kotphunga kot ngah’in anapang jin ahi.
\v 22 Chuche lai chun hongcha kelkot dung ngah dinga kilhengdoh miho mong mong chu mihem 212 alhinguvin ahi; chule amaho hi akhangguiyu kisimna’a akho kho uva kisim sohkei ahiuve. David le mitva neipa Samuel chun amaho hi akitah jeh’uva apu apateu ho chu hitobang apan mun’uva hi apansah lhon ahiuve.
\v 23 Hijeh a chu amaho le son chilhahho chu Pakai Hou-In, ponbuh’a Hou-In kelkot phung dung ngah’a in-ngah’a apansah’u ahiye.
\v 24 Hiche kelkot dunga kot ngah’a pang ho chu niso lam, nilhum lam, Sahlam le lhang lam’a pang sohkeiyuva, mun lia pang ahiuvin ahi.
\v 25 Amaho kithopi din ainkoteu, akho mun cheh’a hunguva nisagi gia amaho hi ahung panhu jing jeng uvah ahi.
\v 26 Kelkot ngah’a pang lamkai cheh Levi mi li ho chu indan jouse leh Pathen Hou-In sunga thil kibol jouse ngah’a jong pang ahiuve.
\v 27 Amaho hi Pathen Hou-In kimvel a geh jiuva, hitia hi amaho chunga in-nga kiti mong mong chu kikoiya, jingkah seh leh kot ahon jiu ahi.
\v 28 Kelkot ngah’a pang mi phabep khat chu Hou-In kinbolna kimangji manchah thil le lo simtoh’in apang jiuvin ahi; ijeh-inem itileh hitobang thilkeo ho chu akilah doh le akikoi lut chan’a amanlouna dinga simtoh ji ji ngai monga ahi.
\v 29 Midang ho jong chu thilkeo dang le manchah thil thengho, changbong ding le lengpitwi, thaotwi, gimnamtuui le adang dang lhutnam ding anamtuui ho vetup din apansah’uvin ahi.
\v 30 Hinlah thempuho chu lhutnam ding gimnamtui chohhal din apansah’uve.
\v 31 Levi mi Mattithiah kitipa leh Korah insung kon Shallum chapa apeng masapen pa chu changlhah pheng semna din avaibol’in apangin ahi.
\v 32 Chujongleh Kohath phunga kon mi phabep jong chu cholngah nikho seh leh todoh ding changlhah semin apanguvin ahi.
\v 33 Levi miho lah a tumging/lathem tah tah ho chu Hou-In sung dan’a acheng den jenguvin ahi. Amaho hi Hou-In kinbolna ho’a ongthol’in aum theiyuve;ijeh-inem itileh amaho hi asun ajan a lasa pang pang jengji ahiuvin ahi.
\v 34 Mi hichengse hi Jerusalem Levi miho apu apauva a insung lhah cheh’a phung upa jeng ahiuve.
\v 35 Gibeon pa Jeiel chu Gibeon khopi anachengin ahi. Ajinu min chu Maacah ahin,
\v 36 Chule achapa apeng masapen chu Abdon ahiye. Jeiel chapa te adang ho chu Zur, Kish, Baal, Ner, Nadab,
\v 37 Gedor, Ahio, Zechariah, chule Mikloth ahiuve.
\v 38 Mikloth hi Shimeam pa ahiye. Inko hijat hi Jerusalem khopia ki-inmai ngatto cheh’in anachenguve.
\v 39 Ner hin Kish ahingin, Kish in Saul ahinge. Saul’in Jonathan, Malkishua, Abinadab, chule Eshbaal ahinge.
\v 40 Jonathan chu Merib-Baal pa ahin, chule Merib-Baal chu Micah pa ahiye.
\v 41 Micah chapa te chu Pithon ahin, Melech ahin, Tahrea ahin, chule Ahaz ahiye.
\v 42 Ahaz hi Jadah pa ahi. Jadah chu Alemeth, Azmaveth, chule Zimri pa ahi. Zimri chu Moza pa ahi.
\v 43 Moza chu Binea pa ahi. Binea chapa chu Rephaiah ahin, Rephaiah chapa chu Eleasah ahin, chule Eleasah chapa chu Azel ahiye.
\v 44 Azel hin chapa gup ahingin, aminu chu Azrikam, Bokeru, Ishmael, Sheriah, Obadiah, chule Hanan ahiuve. Amaho chengse hi Azel chapa te jeng ahiuve.
\c 10
\s1 Saul Thi
\p 
\v 1 Philistine ten Israel chunga gal ahin bol tauve; chule Philistine te masanga Israel te ajam gam tauvin ahi. Gilboa molsang chunga gal alel’uvin akijam chap jeng tauvin ahi.
\v 2 Philishtineten Saul le achapa te ajamnauva apha uvin, hichun achapa thum-Jonathan, Abinadab, chule Malkishua ho chu athat tauve.
\v 3 Saul din gal kisat chu adou hah cheh cheh jeng tan, chuin Philistine thalpi kapthem mihon ma Saul chu amudoh’uvin chule melse tah in amavouvin ahi.
\v 4 Hichun Saul’in jong agalvonpopa jah a aseiyin, “Na chemjam satdoh jengin lang neithat pai jengin, achuti louva ahileh hiche cheptanlou Philistine mite khu hung uvin tin kichepna einei diu ahitai,” ati.
\p Ahivanginla agalvonpopan chutia bol jeng ding chu atijat behseh jeh’in anompon aboldeh tapoi. Hiche jehchun Saul’in jong achemjam akisadoh jengin, achunga alhun akibah lut jenge.
\p 
\v 5 Hichea hi agalvon popanjong Saul thi amudoh phat’in ama jong achemjam chunga akibah lut pai jengin athi pai pai tai.
\v 6 Hitobang hin Saul le achapa mi thum ho chu chumun’a chun abonchan athi khom cheh tauvin, alenggam vaihomna phat sungu jong ahung kichai tai.
\v 7 Hichun Jezreel Phaichama cheng Israel mite leh asepai teu ajam gamtauvin, Saul le achapa te jong athitauve, ti amudoh phat’uvin achennau khopi jouse adalhauvin ajam gam tauve. Chuin Philistine te ahung kitol lut’uvin akhopi ho chu alotauve.
\v 8 Ajing nikho’a Philistine mite chu mithi long chomdoh’a ahunguva ahileh, Saul le achapa te long chu Gilboa molsanga amudoh tauve.
\v 9 Hijeh chun ama hon jong Saul galvon chu ahoh lhauvin, chule alu jong akitan lhah tauve. Chuin ama hon ami lim doi houvu leh Philistia gamsung pumpia mitin henga Saul athi kipana thu alhangsam lele tauvin ahi.
\v 10 ama hon Saul galvon chu a Pathen limsemthu ho Hou-In sunga akoiyun, chule alu jong chu Dagon Hou-In sunga atah’uvin ahi.
\v 11 Hinlah Jabesh- Gilead khoa cheng mitakip’in Philistine ten Saul abolnau ajah doh phat’uvin,
\v 12 Agal-hang lai jouse akipat’uvin Saul tahsa along le achapa te long jouse chu abonchauvin Jabesh khoa ahinpo lut sohkeiyuvin ahi. Chujongleh agubuh jouseu chu Jabesh khopia gangpi phung noiya avuiyun, nisagi sungin an angol’uvin ahi.
\v 13 Hitobang tah hin Saul chun Pakai thupeh anit pon, chule gaochang mi pou adong len, iti chon ding ham, ti doh ding agopon ahi. Hiche jeh a chu Pakaiyin ama chu athadoh’a, lenggam chu Jesse chapa David joh apeh ahitai. \x + \xo 10:13 \xt 1 Samuel 13:8-14; 15:1-24; \xt Thempu Dan 19:31; 20:6; 1 Samuel 28:7,8\x*
\c 11
\s1 Israel Chunga David Lenga Akipansah
\p 
\v 1 Hichun Israel mipite chu Hebron khopia David heng ah chun ahung uvin, keiho hi nangma tahsa tah le thisan kahiuve atiu vin ahi.
\v 2 Masang Saul leng ana hi laia jong nangma hi Israel te gal lamkai ana hijing jeng nahi, chule Pakai na Pathen'in nasei pih banga nangma hi Israel mipi kelngoi chingpha le lamkai dia lhendoh nahi.
\v 3 Hiti chun Hebron mun’a chun David in Pakai le Israel upaho masang ah kitepna theng ana sem in ahi. Hichea Pakaiyin Samuel kom’a anasei bang chun David chu Israel te dia leng dingin thaonu ana hin ahi.
\v 4 Chujouvin David le Israel mipi te chun Jerusalem chulai phat’a jebus tiajong ana kihe mun chu ana nokhum un anasat uve. Hilai chu Jebus mite gamnei dihtah te chen na gam ahi. \x + \xo 11:4 \xt Joshua 15:63; Thutan Vaihom Ho 1:21\x*
\v 5 Chule Jebus miten David chu akhopi sung’u alut ding ana nom povin ahi. Ahivanginla David in Zion kulpi tua David khopi tia kihe mun lai chu ana lotan ahi.
\v 6 David in asepai miho kom’a hitin asei e. Koi hijongleh Jebus mite kisat pia hinthat masa pen aum leh ka sepai jalamkai luboh’a pang ding ahi ati. Hichun Jebus mite hinsat’a that masapen in Joab kitipa David sopinu Zuriah chapa chu ahung hitoh kilhonin, David gal lamkai panmun masapen chu ana chang tan ahi.
\v 7 David in kulpi chu chenna in, amangin hichu David khopi tin akikou e.
\v 8 David in akhopi chu nisolam’a pat avel dung jouse chu akehlet be in ana semtoh in ahi. Chule Joab in amoh chengse chu ana semphan ahi.
\v 9 Hatchungnung Pakaiyin apan pi jih’in David thaneina chu ahung hatdoh cheh cheh jengin ahi.
\s1 David Dinga Gal-Hang Ho
\p 
\v 10 Amaho hi David galhang lamkai’a pang Israel mipi toh kitho khom a Pakaiyin ana kitepna banga David aleng diuva hin tungdoh ding ho chu ahiuve.
\v 11 David gal-hang lamkai minthang ho chu hiche ho hi ahiuve. Amasapen chu ahile Jashobeam kitipa Hachmon mi David gal hat mi thumho lah a lamkai ahi. Amapa hin achemjam mangcha in akidoupi galmi mi jathum chu khatvei in ana that jou in ahi.
\v 12 Anina pen chu ahileh Ahoah son chilhah Dodai chapa Eleazar ahi.
\v 13 Amapa hi Pas-dam'mim a Philistine te ana kisat lai’u chun galmun’a hi David toh ana kitho khom lhon ahi. Chule hiche galmun hi sakol chang dimset ana ke khah jeh chun Israel mite chu anajam tauve.
\v 14 Ahivangin Eleazar le David hi galmun’a kon nung chon louvin Philistine mite chu anasat lhonin ahi. Chule Pakaiyin amani ana huhdoh in minthang tah in galjona sangtah jong ana chang lhon e.
\v 15 Sepai lamkai minthang somthum lah a thum ho chu David Adulam songkoa anaum lai chun Raphiam phaicham a Philistine sepai ho toh ana kimutouvin ahi.
\v 16 David hi chuche phatlai chun akulpi sunga ana um'in ahi. Chule Philistine miten Bethlehem khopi anatou phaovin ahi.
\v 17 David in amite jah a chun hitin aseije, Ohe koitobang eingailu toukhat aum a hiche Bethlehem kelkot phunga twitheng khu eigathal peh thei hile tin aseije .
\v 18 Hichun galhat lamkai thumho chun Philistine bang chu apal keh un, Bethlehem kulpia um twi chu David don dingin ahinle choi pih uve. Ahivangin David in hiche twi chu don louvin Pakai a ding joh in ana katdoh in ahi.
\v 19 Pathen'in hiche twi hi kadon louding ahi. Ajeh chu hiche twi hi ahinkho phal ngam’a twi thal a che ho thisan mantam tah toh kibang ahi tin aseijin, David in twi chu anadon pon ahi. Hichu galhang mithum ho natoh lolhin na vetsahna ahi.
\v 20 Abi'shai hi Joab sopipa lamkai somthum ho lah a pang ahi. Amapa hin achem jam keoseh mangchan akidoupi agalmi mi jathum jen chu ana that jouvin ahi. Hichea kon chun galhat mithum ho banginahung minthang tan ahi.
\v 21 Abi'shai hi galhat mithum ho lah a apan jou lou vang'in mi somthum ho lah a hin lamkai minthang tah khat ahi.
\v 22 Jehoiada chapa Benaiah kiti galhang tah Kabzeel kho a kon mi khat jong ana um e, Amapa hin mihat tah ho natoh jong aboldoh in ahi hiche lah a chu Moab mite galhang mini jong ana that in; chule buhbang lhah lai ni jingkah in jong Keipi bahkai khat jong ana that e.
\v 23 Aman achang seh in khetbuh mai mangchan Egypt galhang milentah asan dan feet sagi le akeh khat’a sang tengcha lentah kichoija galvon lhingset’a kivon pa chu ana that in ahi. Benneah in Egypt mipa tengcha chu alahpeh in, ama thanan anei e.
\v 24 Hitobang thil nasatah ahinbol doh’a kon hin mi minthang galhang thumho banginahung loupi doh e.
\v 25 Hiti chun ama hi mi thumho lah a apan lou vang'in somthum ho sang'in, jana sangtah ana chang in chule David in ama vengtup a lamkai din apan sah tan ahi.
\v 26 David sepai mihat ho chu ahileh Joab sopipa Asahel toh Bethlehem kho a kon Dodo chapa Elha'nan toh ahiuve.
\v 27 Harod kho kon Shammoth le Pelon mi Helez jong ahi.
\v 28 Teko'a khoa Ikkesh chapa Ira jong ahin, Anathoth kho a mi Abi-zer jong ahi.
\v 29 Hushath mi Sibbecai ahin Ahoh kho a kon Ilai jong ahi.
\v 30 Netoph'ah mi Ma'harai ahin, Netophiah mi Ba'anah chapa Heled jong ahi.
\v 31 Benjamin chate gamsung Gib'eah kho a Ribai chapa Ithai jong ahin, chule Pirathon kho a kon Bena'iah jong ahi.
\v 32 Gash luidung a kon Hurai jong ahin, Ar'bath kho a kon Abi'el jong ahi.
\v 33 Baha'rum khoa mi Az'maveth jong ahin, Sha'al'bon kho a mi Eli'ahba jong ahi;
\v 34 Gizon kho a kon Hashem ahin, Harar khoa mi Shagee chapa Jonathan jong ahi,
\v 35 Harar khoa mi mama Sachar chapa Ahi'am ahin, Ur chapa Eli'phal jong ahi;
\v 36 Mecherath kho a mi Hepher ahin, Pelon mi Ahi'jah jong ahi,
\v 37 Carmel kho a Hezro ahin,Ezbai chapa Na'arai ahi,
\v 38 Nathan sopipa Jo'el ahin,Hagri chapa Mibhar ahi,
\v 39 Ammon mi Zelek ahin, Be'eroth kho mi Na'harai ahi, ama hi Zeru'iah chapa galvonpoa pang ahi,
\v 40 Ithir kho kon Ira ahin, Ithir kho a mi ma ma Gareb ahi;
\v 41 Hit mi Uri'ah ahin, Ahlai chapa Zabad jong ahi ,
\v 42 Reuben phung a kon Shiza chapa Ad'ina ahin, ama jong hi Reuben chate lah a lamkai khat ahin, Sepai som thum apui ye,
\v 43 Maacah chapa Hanan ahin,Mathan mi Josh'aphat ahi,
\v 44 Asterath kho a mi Uzzi'a ahin Aro'er mi Shama le Je-i-el ahilhon e,
\v 45 Shimri chapa Jedi'a-el le asopipa Joha ahilhonin, Tiz kho mi ahi cheh lhon e,
\v 46 Mahav mi Eli'el ahin, chule El'na-am chapa teni Jer'ibai le Joshavi'ah ahilhon e, chule Moab mi Ithmah jong ahi,
\v 47 Chujongleh Mezoba kho mi Eli'el le Obed toh chule Ja-asi'el ahiuve.
\c 12
\s1 David Leng Ahina Dinga Panpi Ho
\p 
\v 1 Kish chapa Saul kom Ziklag mun a ana kisel lai a David toh ana umkhom ho chu galhang mi David toh gal anasat khom ho chu ahiuve.
\v 2 Hiche miho hi Benjamin phung a kon Saul sopite ahiuvin thalpi kap them cheh chule akhut jetle vei mangcha thei a songchang bom kap them cheh mi ahiu ve.
\v 3 Gabiah mi Shemah chapa Ahiezar hi amaho dia lamkai pipu pen ahin amanoi bantah a lamkai chu Joash ahi. Chule Azmaoth chapa teni Pelet le Jeziel, Bareah le Anathoth kho a kon Jehu jong ahi.
\v 4 Gebeon a kon Ishmiah kitipa hi galhang somthum ho lah a lamkai le kinthang pen ahi. Chule Gederah kho a kon Jerrmiah, Jahaziel, Johanan le Jozabad ahiuve.
\v 5 Haruph kho a kon Eluzai, Jeremoth, Beliah, Shemariah le Sephatiah ahiuve.
\v 6 Korahites phung a kon Elkanah , Issiah, Azarel, Joezor le Jashobeam ahi.
\v 7 Gedor a kon Jeroham chapa teni Joelah le Zebediah ahi.
\v 8 David gamthip noi kulpi a anaum laiyin Gad nammite galhang galbol them cheh ho chun ana pan piu vin ahi. Amaho chu lumchoije le tengcha kho themcheh Keipi bahkai bang a gin umtah chule sakhi golpai bang a chom jangkhai jeng ahiuve.
\v 9 Ezer chu lamkai pipu pen ahin anichan na chu Obadiah ahin, athum chan na chu Eliab ahi.
\v 10 Mishmamnah chu ali chan na ahin chule Jeremiah chu angana ahi.
\v 11 Agup channa chu Attai ahin, chule sagi chan na chu Eliel ahi.
\v 12 Aget channa chu Johanan ahin chule ako channa chu Elzabed ahi.
\v 13 Jeremiah chu asom channa ahin, Macbannai chu somle khat chan na ahi.
\v 14 Amaho hi Gad mite galhang lamkai pipu cheh ngen ahiuvin ahi. Chule anem nung pen chu sepai jakhat ahiuvin asang jo pen ho chu sangkhat vel ahiuve .
\v 15 Hiche mite ho chu kum kihei kumbul a Jordan vadung letlha hel la twi hunglon chun vapam achen nao mun a kon'in solam le lhumlam gam a ana homkhen uvin ahi.
\v 16 Chule adang ho Benjamin le Judah phung mite chu David kulpi a chun ahungun ahi.
\v 17 Chuin David jong amaho kimu pin ahung pot in, hitin asei e. Kipah tah a keima kithopi dia hung nahiu le eiho loikhat ihiuve. Amavang kagal mite angsung a keima pedoh ding a hung nahiule vang kapului-u Pathen'in nangho chunga gotna napeh diu ahi.
\v 18 Chuin Amasai kitipa somthum ho lah a lamkai pa chu lhagao houpi na achangin hitin asei e, “Jesse chapa David keiho nang a kahiuve, nagma lam a pang ding kahiuve, chamna le phatthei nan najui jing hen chule nangma nakithopi jouse jong lolhing uhen ajeh chu Pathen'in nangma napanpi ahi.” Hiti chun David in amaho chu akiloipin asepaite chung a lamkai dingin jong apansah tan ahi.
\v 19 David Philistine te toh kithokhom a gal ana konlai chun Manasseh chate Israel sepai ten jong ana pan piu vin ahi. Ahivangin Philistine sepai lamkai ho chun David hi nikhokhat le Saul lang joh a hung pang a eiho suh gam le elol u tan a hung pang thei ahi atiuvin David toh kilhon khom jing chu ana nom tapouvin anasol mang tauve.
\v 20 David ziglak a ana kile Manasseh chaten David anajop ho chu ahile Adnah , Jozbed, Jedial, Michael Jozabed , Elihu le Zillethai ahiuve. Amaho lamkai nanoi a Manasseh phung a kon sepai mi sangkhat ahiuve.
\v 21 Hiti chun amaho hin David chung a gal hinbol gamho jouse chu hatah in ana dou un ana kisat piuvin ahi. Chule amaho hi mihangsan tah galhang lamkai thei cheh ahiuvin ahi.
\v 22 Chule aniseh in David lang a pang ding le akithopi ding sepai akibe jingin, Pathen sepai tampi bang a ahung umdoh kahsen mi ahung kikhom jing e.
\v 23 Pakai thupeh dungjui a saul lenggam vaipohna pumpi David chansah ding a Hebron khopia hung kikhom doh sepai ami mong monga akihop jat-u hicheng hi anahiuve.
\v 24 Juda phung sung a kon galvon le tengcha tho thei cheh mi sang gup le jaget alhing e.
\v 25 Chule Simeon phung a galhang galsat thei cheh agom a mi sang sagi le jakhat alhing e.
\v 26 Levi phung a kon galhang mi sangli le jagup alhing in ahi.
\v 27 Hichea hin Aaron insung a kon Jehoaida lamkai nanoi a mi sangthum le jasagi alhing e.
\v 28 Chule Zadok kiti galbol mihang santah insung a kon'in jong gallamkai cheh mi somni le ni alhing e.
\v 29 Benjamin phung a kon a Saul inkote galsat sepai mi sangthum ahiuvin chule amaho lah a atam jo hi Benjamin'insungmi a kon Saul lam a pang ana hi jing uve.
\v 30 Ephriam phung a kon'in jong galsat hangsan tah mi sang somnile get alhing in chule ama hung kondohna phunggui sung a dia jong jaum tah le mi minthang cheh ahiuve.
\v 31 Manasseh namkeh khat Jordan lhumlam a kon sepai sang somle sang get umho chun David leng ahung hi nadingin ana kitho piu vin ahi.
\v 32 Issachar mite le a insungmi a kon'in jong lamkai mi jani ana lhing e. Hiche miho jouse hi Israel te chung a thil hunglhung ding le phat kihei dan ho hetthem nanei cheh mi ahiuve.
\v 33 Zebulun phung a kon'in jong galbol a them tah galhang sepai mi sang nga alhing e. Amaho hi David toh kitho khom a galsat dia galman chah toh kigo sa cheh ahiu vin ahi.
\v 34 Naphtali phung a kon'in jong galhang cheh galman chah lhingset a lumpho le tengcha mangcha thei sepai lamkai mi sangkhat le galsat sepai mi sangthum le jasagi alhing uve.
\v 35 Dan phung sung a kon'in jong galmun a dia kigo sadem a galsat ding mi sang somni le sang get le jagup alhing uve.
\v 36 Asher phung a kon'in jong galbol dan kichuh sepai sang somli jong galsat dia kigo sa ahiuve.
\v 37 Chule Jordan vadung nisolam a kon'in jong Gad mite le Reuben phung mite chule Manasseh nam kehkhat chu galsat dia manchah chom cheh kichoi lhingset sepai mi sang jakhat le sang somni alhing uve.
\v 38 Hebron mun hinjon a galsat dia kigosadem a um sepai tampi ho ahiuvin chule Isareal mipi jousen jong David chu Isareal pumpia a leng dingin adeisah sohkei uve.
\v 39 Chuin a insungmi asopiten David chu vailhun na ding thil ijakai agong toh uvin nithum sung in David toh ann nehkhom le lengpitwi donkhom na anei uve.
\v 40 Avel a um Isachar, Zebulun le Naphtali ho chengin jong sangan le sangongsao chule sakol pol le bongchal ho chu neh ding poh nan amang chaovin ahi. Chule neh ding don ding changlhah hihen theichang ga changlhah, bongchal, kelngoi le kelcha ho geiyin golnop bol nadin ahinpolut uvin ahi. Hichu Israel pumpia ding a kipa golnop loupi tah ana hin ahi.
\c 13
\s1 Kirjath-Jearim Akon Pathen Thingkong Ahin Tollut
\p 
\v 1 David in asepai sangkhat chung a lamkai ho leh jakhat chung a lamkai ho chu thu adong toh sohkei in ahi.
\v 2 Chuin aman Israel mite jouse kom a chun hitin asei e, “Nangho le Pakai Pathen lunglam ahile Israel mite chenna jouse a Thempu ho le levi mite jaona a ibon chaova iki-khop khom soh theina diuvin thu lhangsapna nei u hite,” ati.
\v 3 Saul lengvai poh lai in Pathen kitepna thingkong chu nahsah mon ana um jongleh tuhi anung lahphat tah chu ahi.
\v 4 Akihoukhom mipi jousen hichu pha asah utoh kilhonin abon chaovin boldin kinopto na anei taove.
\v 5 Hiti chun David in Pathen thingkong chu nung put lut kit na dingin Kiriath Jeriam mun a kon'in muntin'a Israel mite aumnao Egypt lhanglam gam shehor vadung a pat chule sahlam gam Lebohamath khopi vel dung a kon abon'uva ahung kikhop khomna diuvin kouna aneiyin ahi. \x + \xo 13:5 \xt 1 Samuel 7:1,2\x*
\v 6 Pathen thingkong nunglah kit nadingin David le Israel mite chun Judah gam Baalah Kiriath jeriam tiajong kikou mun a chun ana cheu vin ahi. \x + \xo 13:6 \xt Potdohbu 25:22\x*
\v 7 Chuin ama hon Pathen thingkong chu Abinadab insung a kon'in ahin la doh un bongkang thah leh a akoi uve. Chule hiche bongkang chu Uzzah le Ahio tenin ahin tol lhonin ahi.
\v 8 Hichun David le Israel mipite chun Pathen ang ah kipah le thanom tah in la asauvin, selangdah le semjang asaiyun, khongle dah chule kipa khutbeh toh thon saki pengkul ana mut uvin ahi.
\s1 Uzzah Kitha Chule Pathen Thingkong Obed-Edom In Muna Kidalha
\p 
\v 9 Ahivangin ama hon Nacon changphol lai ahin phah u chun bongchal chu ahung kipal lhun Uzzah in Pathen thingkong chu tuh dingin akhut ana lhang in ahi.
\v 10 Uzzah in Pathen thingkong chung a akhut ajah a pat in achung a Pakai lunghan na ana chutan hijeh chun Pathen'in Uzzah adeng in ama angsung a ana thiden tan ahi.
\v 11 Pakaiyin Uzzah chung a alunghan na aphon jal jeh chun David jong analung nalheh jengin ahi. Hijeh chun David in hilai mun chu Perez- Uzzah asah in ahi, hichu Uzzah kisuh gep namun tin tuni gei in akikou in ahi.
\v 12 Chule David kicha tah a aumphat chun Pathen adongin aseitai. Pathen thing kong chu eti keiman kaga nunglah kit a kakom'a kakoi ngam ding ham ati.
\v 13 Hijeh chun David injong Pathen thingkong chu David khopia poh lut joh sangin Gath mipa Obed-edom insung a analhut jotan ahi.
\v 14 Hiti chun Pathen thingkong chu lhathum Obed-edom insung a ana umden in hiche sung chun Pakaiyin Obed-edom insung mite chu anatohnalam cheh uva phatthei anaboh in ahi. \x + \xo 13:14 \xt 1 Thusimbu 26:4,5\x*
\c 14
\s1 Hiram In David Ahetdoh
\p 
\v 1 Tyre gam a leng Hiram in asottole a pang thingthem bol le songkhen them ho chu Cedar thing ho a David inpi sah pih dingin ana sol in ahi.
\v 2 Chule Pakaiyin israel pumpi a lengdia atun a amite Israel te ding a alenggam phattheina aboh chu David in jong ana geldoh tan ahi.
\v 3 Chujouvin David in Jerusalem a chun ji akipui be in chanu le chapa jong tampi anei kit in ahi.
\v 4 Amaho hi David in Jerusalem’a anahinsa achapa te chu ahiuve: Shammu, Sobad, Nathan, Solomon
\v 5 Ibhar, Elishua, Elpelet
\v 6 Noqah, Nepheg, Japhia
\v 7 Elishma, Beeliada chule Eliphelet ahiuve.
\s1 David In Philistine Ajo
\p 
\v 8 David Israel pumpia a leng chan ding chu Philistine miten ajah phat uvin Philistine sepai ho chu David man dingin ahung kon uvin ahi, David in jong hiche thu ajah phat chun amaho kimaito pi din akondoh pai kit in ahi.
\v 9 Hiti chun philistine sepai ho chun gang tah in Raphiam phaicham chu ahin nokhum pai jengun ahi.
\v 10 Hichun David in Pathen adongin, “Hiche Philistine te khu gasat leng achung uva galjona neichan sah ding ham?” ati. Chuin Pakaiyin adonbut in, “Chenlang gasat in achung uva galjo na nachan ding ahi,” ati.
\v 11 Hichun David le asepai te chu Baal-Perazim lam jon in akitol uvin Philistine te chu agasat uvin ana jou tauve. Chuin David in hitin asei e, “Pathen'in kamelma te chung a twisuh long bang a kalonkhum na din eina mang chai,” ati. Hijeh chun hichelai mun hi Baal-perazam ana kisah in ahi.
\v 12 Chuin Philistine te anajam uvin milim doi Pathen semthu ana dalhah hou chu David in ana hal vam sah in ahi.
\v 13 Ahivangin Philistine te chun hetman lou kah in phaicham chu ahin nokhum paikit uvin ahi.
\v 14 Hijeh chun David injong ipi bol ding hitam tin Pathen adong kit in ahile Pathen'in amaho nungjui kit lou in amasang lam uva kon a ahinle del khum a balsom thingphung a hinno khum un tin asei e.
\v 15 Nangman thingleh vum lang a pat mitampi kijot kengto gin najah teng pot inlang galsat pan jengin ajeh chu Pathen'in Philistine sepaite satgam nadia nangma nahin panpi ding chu avetsah ahi.
\v 16 Hiti chun David in jong Pathen thupeh banginabollin ahile Philistine sepaite chu Gibeon a kipat in Gezer chan in ana del jam suh in ahi.
\v 17 Chuin muntin jousea David ahung minthan phat in Pakaiyin David chu namjouse te ginle ja in aum sah tan ahi.
\c 15
\s1 David In Kipah Tah’a Pathen Thingkong Jerusalem Ahinlhut
\p 
\v 1 David in akhopi a chun injong tampi anasa in chule Pathen thingkong koi nading jong ponbuh phatah ana song in ahi.
\v 2 Hichun David in hitin asei e Pathen thingkong pudia chu Pakai deilhen Levi mite tailou chu akin bol a pangthei louding ahi ati. \x + \xo 15:2 \xt Danbu Ni Na 10:8\x*
\v 3 Hichun David in Pakai thingkong koina dingmun semna a pulut dingin Jerusalem khopi a um Israel mite chu ana kou in ahi.
\v 4 Hiche a anakikou miho chu ahile Aaron thempu le Levi chate ho ahiuve.
\v 5 Uriel lamkai na a kon'in Kohath nambah ami jakhat le somni ahin ,
\v 6 Asaiah lamkai na a Meraei nambah akon mi janile somni ahi,
\v 7 Joel lamkai na akon Gerahon nambah mi jale somthum alhing uve,
\v 8 Elizaphan son chilhah akon Shemaiah lamkaina mi jani alhing e,
\v 9 Hebron son chilhah a kon Eliel lamkai na in mi somget alhing uve,
\v 10 Aminadab lamkai na in Uzziel chilhah te chu mi jale som le ni ma alhing uve.
\v 11 Chuin David in thempu ho Zadok le Abiathar chule Levi mite lah a kon'in Uriel, Asaiah, Joel ahin Shemaiah ahin Eliel le Aminadab ho chu akou khom sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 12 David in amaho kom'a chun hitin asei e; “Nangho Levi insung mite dia lamkai pipui nahiu ve. Hijeh chun Israel Pathen pakai thingkong chu akoina ding a kagotna mun a nahin nungput kitna diuvin nangho ahin chule na insungmite cheng nabon un kisutheng un,” ati.
\v 13 Pakaiyina-doh lou jeh’u chun Pakai vantil Pathen lunghan na ichung uva ana chu’in Levi mite chun thingkong chu nana pohlut thei lou-u ahi.
\v 14 Hijeh chun thempu ho le Levi mite jouse chun Israel Pathen Pakai thingkong Jerusalem mun’a putdoh nadin kilhai na ana nei uvin ahi.
\v 15 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose athuhil bang chun Levi miten Pathen thingkong chu moljol in alengkou un ahin pu uvin ahi. \x + \xo 15:15 \xt Potdohbu 25:14\x*
\v 16 Hichun David in jong lamkai ho chu thu apen Levi mite lasathem le tumging them hon kipa lasah a tumging le semjang sai a khutbeh gintho dingin asei e.
\v 17 Chuin Levi hon jong Joel chapa Heman Levi tetoh sopi Merari nambah sung a kon Berekiah chapa ahin, Kushaiah chapa Ethan ho cheng ana pan sah uvin ahi.
\v 18 Chule amaho noi bantah a dingin Zacharaiah, Zaaziel, Shemiramoth, Jehid, Unni, Eliab, Bennaiah, Massaiah, Mattithiah, Eliphileh, Mikniah le kotkhah ngah a pang Obed-edom le Jeiel ho chu ana pansah uvin ahi.
\v 19 Tumging them lah a Heman , Asaph le Ethan ho chu sumeng semjang sai dingin ana lheng uvin,
\v 20 Chule Zechariah, Aziel, Shemiramoth, Jehiel, Unni, Eliab, Measaiah le Benaiah ho cheng chu selang dah sai din ana lheng doh uvin ahi.
\v 21 Chule Mittithiah, Elipelehu, Mikneiah, Obed-edom, Jeiel chule Azaziah ho chu la aw lhingsetna sahna kimang semjang saidin apan sah uve.
\v 22 Chuin Levi te lah a lamkai Kenaiah hi lasah lambolthei tah ahijeh chun la lamkai din apan sah uve.
\v 23 Chule Pathen thingkong vengtup dingin Berekaiah le Elkanah chu ana pansah uve.
\v 24 Shebanaiah, Josephhat, Nethanel, Amasai, Zecharaiah, Beniah le Eliezer ho cheng hin Pathen thingkong mai a kitol uva saki a kisem pengkul amut diu ahi, chule Obed-edom le Jehiah chu Pathen thingkong kotngah in apan sah uve.
\v 25 David le Israel upate chule sepai lamkai pipuho chun Pakai kitepna thingkong chu Jerusalem a ahin pohlut a loupi tah a kipa pi dingin Obed-edom inpia chun ana cheuve.
\v 26 Chule Pathen'in Levi mite akithopi a, ama hon Pakai kitepna thingkong ahin pohlut jeh u chun bongchal sagi le kelngoi sagi kilhai nan anathat uve.
\v 27 David le Levi mite Pakai thingkong pua pang ahin, lasa a pang ho le la lamkai Kenaniah ho chu tupat ponnem in ana kivon uve. David jong chun thempu ho lengban khat jong ana kiban in ahi.
\v 28 Hiti chun Israel mite chun kipana aw thong’a sampum le sumkon gin le saki mutgin chule khutbeh beng ginle semjang saiging tho in Pakai kitepna thingkong chu ahin pulut uvin ahi.
\v 29 Pakai kitepna thingkong David khopia ahin pohlut u chun, Saul chanu Michal in in bang kot apat ahin vetsuh le leng David kipa thanop thoa achop le chu amun ana japi in ahi.
\c 16
\s1 David In Kilhaina Thilto Abol
\p 
\v 1 Hichun ama hon Pathen thingkong chu David in akoina dia ponbuh hoitah ason namun a chun ahin polut uvin ahi. Chua chun ama hon Pathen a kilhai na pumgo thilto jong ana kat uvin ahi.
\v 2 David in kilhaina kin aneijou in amite chu Pakai min'in phatthei aboh in ahi.
\v 3 Chujouvin aman ami Israel te numei pasal abonchauvin changlhah alhang a kisem ahin, lengpithei ga’a kisem nehthei ana peh ahi.
\v 4 David in Levi mite chu Pakai thingkong maiya Israel Pathen Pakai phattheina sima, a vahchoi lasah le thangvah dingin mipi jouse lamkai din ana pansah e.
\v 5 Asaph chu amaho lah a lamkai ahin, ama hin lasah na a kimang tumging sumeng kivo ging asai yin ahi. Amaban tah’a chu Zechariah ahin chule ama kithopi dingin Jeiel, Mattithiah, Eliab, Benaiah, Obed-edom le Jeiel ahiuve. Amaho hi semjang le selangdah sai a pang ahiuve.
\v 6 Chule Pathen thingkong kitepna masang a chun thempu Benaiah le Jahaziel chun tanglouvin sumkon ana mut lhonin ahi.
\v 7 David in hiche nikho chun Asaph le ami Levi te chutoh Pakai a kipa na thangvah na lasah na ana peu vin ahi.
\v 8 Pakai chu thangvah na peuvin chule aloupina seiphong uvin vannoi leiset pumpin athibol jouse hecheh hen,
\v 9 Thangvah toh thon ama vahchoi un chule namtin jouse chung a athilbol kidang ho hillhang uvin,
\v 10 Amintheng chu hapah in kipapi un, eiho Pakai mite ehiuve,
\v 11 Tantih neilouvin Pakai thahatna chu hol jingun lang hou uvin,
\v 12 Thil kidang tampi le datmo umtah aboldoh ho leh athu tan naho geldoh jingun,
\v 13 Nangho alhacha Israel chate ho chule Jacob son chilhah anam deilhen mite ho,
\v 14 Ama hi eiho Pakai Pathen ahi, Ama thupeh dihtah hi vannoi jousen amu ding ahi.
\v 15 Aman a-itih khang chan in jong akitepna agel doh jingin ahi,
\v 16 Hiche hi aman Abraham toh kitepna asem chu ahin chule Isaac heng a kitepna ana neichu ahi, \x + \xo 16:16 \xt Semtilbu 12:7; \xt Semtilbu 26:3\x*
\v 17 Aman hichu Jacob heng a Israel mite toh a-itih khang gei a tonsot a dia kitepna thulhuh le suhdetna ana nei ahi. \x + \xo 16:17 \xt Semtilbu 28:13\x*
\v 18 “Nangma chan ding goulo nading Canaan gam chu kapeh ding nahi,” ati.
\v 19 Aman hiche aseilai chun nangmaho Canaan gam'a hon lhomcha a khopem bang a nana umlai u ahi, ati.
\v 20 Hiti chun amaho chu namkhat apat namkhat in anavah uvin chule lenggam khat apat gamdang a ana vah leu ve,
\v 21 Chujongleh aman amaho chu koima suhgentheina le bolgimna ana neisah pon, amaho jeh in leng dang ho joh thugah na ananei jon ahi, \x + \xo 16:21 \xt Semtilbu 20:3-7\x*
\v 22 Kami lhenchomte natohkhah thei loudiu chule kathemgao ho jong nasuh genthei loudiu ahi,
\v 23 Leiset pumpin Pakai chu vahchoi hen chule aniseh in ami huh hingna thupha chu seiphong leuvin,
\v 24 Namtin vaipi lah a athilbol loupi ho phongjal un, chule athilbol kidang ho mitin vaipi hetsah un,
\v 25 Pakai chu thunei pen ahin amin loupi vahchoi dia lomtah ahi. Chule Pathen dang jouse sang a gin le jadia lom ahi,
\v 26 Namtin vaipi dang ho hou hi semthu milim doi Pathen ahi, eiho Pakai vang hi vanlaijol sempa ahi,
\v 27 Jana le lalna jouse le thahatna chule kipana Pakai ama kom'a um ahi,
\v 28 Vannoi namtin vaipin Pakai thahat na le aloupi je chu hecheh hen,
\v 29 Pakai chu loupina jouse chang dia lom ahi, amuntheng dung jousea Pakai chu thilpeh toh thon houvun,
\v 30 Leiset mite jouse Pakai masang a tijan kithing jeng hen, leiset jong linglouhel in dettah in ding jing hen,
\v 31 Van'a le leiya kipa thanop nan lodim soh hen chule Pakai vaihomna namtin vaipi jousea seiphong leuvin,
\v 32 Twikhanglen le asung a cheng jousen jong avah choina sam u hen chule loulai dungle mimle chang ho jong kipah thanom in hung pohjal jeng uhen,
\v 33 Gammang thingphung jouse jong kipah lasah in kilingdoh soh hen, Pakai chu leiset na thutan’a ahung teng,
\v 34 Pakai chu aphatna jallin thangvah na peuvin, ama a um tahsan umtah mi ngailutna chun tonsot'in athoh jing e, \x + \xo 16:34 \xt 2 Thusimbu 5:13; 7:3; Ezra 3:11; Labu 100:5; 106:1; 107:1; 118:1; 136:1; Jeremiah 33:11\x*
\v 35 “O Pathen eihuh hing paovin namtin vaipi lah a kon'in neipui khom uvin lang neihuhdoh uvin, chuteng nangma mintheng chu kakipa piuva kavah choi diu ahi.
\s1 David In Pathen Thingkong Jenle Dinga Miho Angense
\p 
\v 36 Pakai Israel Pathen chu vahchoiyun ama chu tonsot tonsot gei a hingjing ahi chule amite jousen Pakai chu vahchoi in sam uhen,” Amen.
\v 37 Hiti chun David in Pakai kitepna thingkong a aniseh a angaichat najouse a natong le dingin Asaph le ama mi Levi mite chu ana pansah in ahi.
\v 38 Hiche holah a chun Jeduthun chapa Obed-edom, Hosah le Levi mite misom gup le get chu kotkhah ngah in ana pang uve.
\v 39 Chule David in Zadok thempu le Levi mite chu Gibeon gamsung a Pakai Pathen Houbuh a kimang cha din ana koi in ahi.
\v 40 Pakaiyin Israel te chung a dan thupeh juidia ana nei banginama hon Pakai a jingkah nilhah in kilhaina thilpeh maicham jong ana nei uve,
\v 41 Pakai akitah na le mingailutna tonsot na athohhat na jallin ama thang vah na pe dingin David in Heman le Jeduthun ana lhengdoh un chule midang ana minphah chan jong ana pang uvin ahi.
\v 42 Hiti chun ama hon sumkon mut ginle khutbeh ginle tumging theijat tampi ho mang chan Pathen anavah choi uve, chule Jeduthun chapa chu kotkhah ngah in ana pansah uve.
\v 43 Chujouvin mipi jouse chu ama inlam cheh a ana kileu vin David jong ama inlam a a insung mite phattheiboh dingin ana che tan ahi. \x + \xo 16:43 \xt 2 Samuel 6:19,20\x*
\c 17
\s1 David In Pathen Houna In Sah Ding Anop Vanga, Pathen In Phalpeh Lou
\p 
\v 1 David chu ama inpia ana umlai in Themgao Nathan chu akou in akom'a hitin asei e, “Keimala Cedar thing a kisa innom tah a kachengin, ahivangin Pakai kitepna thingkong vang chu ponbuh a kisa mai mai noi a ana kikoi in ahi.”
\v 2 Nathan in adonbut in, “Nalung a um nagel chan chu bollin ajeh chu Pathen'in naumpi nai.”
\v 3 Ahivangin, hicheni jantah chun Pathen'in Nathan kom'a anasei e,
\v 4 “Chenlang kasohpa David kom'a gahiltan nangma hi keima umna ding munsem ding chu nahipoi’tin ana sei e.”
\v 5 Keiman Egypt gam a kon Israel te kahin pui doh nikho apat tunigei in ka insung a kacheng kha hih laiye,
\p Hiti chun ponbuh a kisong Houbuh munkhat a kon mun chom chom a kana ki chon le jin ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman Israel mite toh kilhon khom ding le kamite kelngoi ching a pang lamkai ho kom'a jong Cedar thing a kisa in eisah pih diu in jong kana sei kha hyh e.
\v 7 Tun nangma chen lang kalhachapa David kom'a hitin gasei tan, “Van Pakai thanei chungnung in hitin aphong doh e,keiman nangma hi hamhing lah a kelngoi ching a napan na’a kon kapuidoh a kami Israel te chung a lamkai dia kapan sah ding nahi, ati.
\v 8 Chule keiman nangma nache namun jousea kalhonpi jing a, nangma masang a namelmate jouse jong kasuh gam jeng ding leiset chung a mi minthang ho bang a namin kakithan sah ding ahi.
\v 9 Chule kamite Israel te ding a achen nadiu munjong kapeh ding dettah a lungmongsel a cheng uva koiman jong asuh ling thei loudiu ahi. Namdang ten jong masang a banga asuhmang kit loudiu ahi.
\v 10 Keiman aphat dungjui a kamite Israel te chung a Lamkai vaihom ding kapan sah jing ding chule namel mateu aboncha kasuh gam ding chuche kal a jong Pakaiyin na lenggam sung u phatthei aboh ding ahi.
\v 11 Nahinkho abei nung a napu napate kom'a dia nache nungteng jong le keiman nadalhah nason nachilhah te lah a nachapa te khat pen kadopsang ding ahi chule alenggam jong lentah a kaphudoh peh ding ahi.
\v 12 Amapa chun keima ding a Hou-In khat eisah peh ding chule keiman alenggam laltouna chu a-itih chan a kaphudet jing ding ahi.
\v 13 Hiche mipa ding a chu keima hi apa kahi a ama chu kachapa hi ding ahi. Nangma masang a mipa chung a kangailutna kana lahdoh bang a, ama chung a hi kanung lah doh louding ahi. \x + \xo 17:13 \xt 2 Crth 6:18; Heb 1:5\x*
\v 14 Keiman ama ka insung a le kagamsung a leng a kapan sah ding chule alenggam laltou na chu atonsot geiya kaphudet pih a longlouva um jing ding ahi,” ati.
\v 15 Hiti chun Nathan ahung kile in Pakaiyin amusah thil hojouse chu David kom'a ahung seipeh tan ahi.
\s1 David Taona Leh Thangvahna
\p 
\v 16 Chuin David alut in Pakai angsung a atao vin hitin asei e, “O Pakai Pathen keima hi koi kahi a chule ka insung mite hi ipi hija hichan gei a neihin puipeh jing u ham?
\v 17 Tun thil hicheng jouse kal val in jong O Pathen, nalhachapa keima khunung a insung thudol khanggui sotpi hunglhung ding jong neisei doh pih in ahi.
\v 18 Hitobang a nalhachapa neijabol na hi nangma kom'a ipi kasei be nahlai ding ham, nalhachapa keima itobang kahi la neihet sohkei ahitai.
\v 19 Nalhachapa keima neigel khoh najal le nalungel lam tah banginkachung a thil loupi tampi mite mutheijin nabol doh in ahi,
\v 20 O Pakai, nang tobang koima dang aumpoi, nangma tobang Pathen dang jong kanei pouve,
\v 21 Nami Israel nam mite tobang leisetna koidang um am? O Pathen, nangma tah in namite asoh chan nagam a kon'in nana huhdoh jeh in namin akithang in ahi, nangman thil kidangtah nabol in namite masang a ding ho jong nana del jam in ahi.
\v 22 Nangman Israel mite chu nangma mite dihtah mong in nana lheng doh in Pakai nangma chu a Pathen u nahitan ahi,
\v 23 O Pakai tunvang keima nalhacha kahitai, keima le ka insungmi chung chang thua nakitepna banginbol jeng tan chule hiche kitepna hi a-itih chan a ding hita hen.
\v 24 Nangma min kiphut doh henlang mijousen tonsot'in jana pecheh hen chule Pakai thanei chungnung pen Israel Pathen chu Israel Pathen ahi mong e tia kisei ding, nalhachapa David insung jeng jong nangma angsung a phudet a um ding ahi.
\v 25 O ka Pathen keima hi nangma ang a ngamtah a hungtao a kahi, ajeh chu nalhachapa keima hi ka in ding neisah peh a lenggam khat neitundoh peh ding chu kicheh tah in neimu sah tai.
\v 26 O Pakai nangma bou Pathen nahi chule hitobang thilpha tampihi nalhachapa kei dingin kitepna nanei e.
\v 27 Tunjong nalhachapa insung phatthei naboh a hichu nalhachapa a ding a a-itih gei a nangma masang a um jing ding ahi. Ajeh chu O Pakai nangma phathei boh chu ipi hijongleh phattheiboh chang jing ding ahi.
\c 18
\s1 David In Alenggam Asuh-Let
\p 
\v 1 Chule David in Philistine te ana kisat pin anajou vin Gath khopi le avel a kho umho jong chu analo in ahi.
\v 2 Chuin David in Moab mite chu ana kisat pin ana joukit in ama khutnoi in aum uvin sum donle kai jong David ana peuvin ahi.
\v 3 David in jong Euphrates luipang a kon thahat tah a ahung kon toulai uvin Zobah lengpa Hadadezer sepai te chu Hemanath chan in anasat in ajouvin ahi.
\v 4 Hiti chun David in kangtalai sangkhat anaman in chule kangtalai tol'a pang mi sang sagi ma aman in keng lamjot sepai sang somni ahin chule kangtalai kai a pang sakol jouse akeng atanpih in kangtalai jakhat kaikham bou akhen in ahi.
\v 5 Chule Aramean mite Damascus khopi a kon a Hadadezer lengpa kithopi dia hung kon ho chu David in mi sang som nile sangni jen ana that in ahi.
\v 6 Hichun David in Aramean gam a Damascus khopi a chun sepai tampi atou sah in, Aramean mite chu David khutnoi in anaum uvin donlekai jong ana peuvin ahi, chule Pakaiyin David chu agal kon nalam jouse a galjona apejing e.
\v 7 David in Hedadezer sepai lamkai ho kipoh sana lum ho jouse chu Jerusalem ah ahin polut'in ahi.
\v 8 Hadadezer khopi Tebah le Cun a chun David in sumeng tampi ahin kilah in chule Solomon in hiche sum-eng ho chu kisilna twi kong le sum-eng khompi le Pathen houna in a manchah ding thil dang sem nan aneiyin ahi. \x + \xo 18:8 \xt 1 Lgt 7:40-47; 2 Thusimbu 4:11-18\x*
\v 9 Hamath lengpa Toi in Zobah lengpa Hadadezer sepaite jouse David in abonchan ajoutai tithu anajan,
\v 10 hichun amapan achapa Joram chu David galjona kipapi dingin anasol in ahi. Ajeh chu Hadadezer hin Toi ana kisat pi jing lai ahi, Joram chun David chu thilpeh tampi sana, sumeng le dangka ho anapen ahi.
\v 11 Leng David in hiche thilpeh hung jouse ahin sumeng le sana namdang mite Edom, Moab, le Amaleke mite kom'a ahinlah doh jouse chu abonchan Pakai adingin ana todoh in ahi.
\v 12 Zeruiah chapa Abishai kitipa chun chikhuh phaicham a chun Edom mite mi sangsom le get jen ana that in ahi. \x + \xo 18:12 \xt Labu 60\x*
\v 13 Chuin aman Edom gamsung a chun sepai atousah in chule Edom mite chu David khutnoi in ana um uve, Hiti chun David chu ache nachan a Pakaiyin galjona apejingin ahi.
\v 14 Chujouvin David chu Israel pumpia lengvai pon apang in ama natoh thilbol ho jouse chu ami Isareal te a ding a thilpha le adih jeng ahi e,
\v 15 Zeruiah chapa Joab chu sepai lamkai in apang in chule Ahilud chapa Jehosaphet chu thuching le lekha sun in ana pang in ahi.
\v 16 Ahitub chapa Zadok le Abiathar chapa Ahimeleche chu thempun apang lhonin chule Seraiah kitipa chu thutanna mun a lekha sun in apang e.
\v 17 Jehoiada chapa Beniah chu lengpa veng a pangho chunga vaipon ana pang e, chule David chapa te chu lengpa kinbol na a vaihom pipun ana pang uve.
\c 19
\s1 David Dinga Thopole Ho Jumna
\p 
\v 1 Phat chomkhat jou a Ammon mite Lengpa Nahash ahung thi chun achapa Hanun chu leng in ahung pang tai.
\v 2 David in, “Keiman Hanun chung a hi kakitah na kapoh doh ding ahi, ajeh chu apa Nahash hi keima chung a akitah jingin ahi,” tin asei e. Hiti chun David in Hanun pa thina jeh a lunghem na akon lungmon sah nadingin asottol le ho asol in ahivangin David sottol leho Ammon gam ahung lhun phat in,
\v 3 Ammon mite lamkai pa chun Hanun kom'ah chun, “Nangman hiche mipite ho hi napa jabolna jal'a hung a nagel mong ham? Hichu hilou a David in amaho hi agam umdan ho vetoh le a chujou tengleh hung kon uva agamsung mite jouse hi nokhum ding lung agot joh ahi,” tin asei e.
\v 4 Chuin Hanun in David sottol leho chu aman in asam u avo peh un chule aponsil hou jong akongjang atobuh dung uva achetan peh in abon chaovin David heng a anung sol tauve.
\v 5 David in amite chunga hitobng thilsoh umchan le asottol leho ajachat naho thu ajah jeh chun Jericho khopi ah chun akhamul u ahung khandoh kah uva tham den uva chujou teng hung kile dingin asei e.
\s1 David In Ammon Mite Leh Syria Mite Ajo
\p 
\v 6 Ammon mite chun, David lungdou na athilbol u ahetdoh phat u chun Hanun le Ammon mite chun Zoab le Aramaacah chule Ram-naharaim gam a kon sakol touthem sepai le kangtalai tampi thalah nadin dangka talent sangsom sagi le sang nga jen ana thot in ahi.
\v 7 Chujongleh ama hon kangtalai sang somthum le ni jong athalah uvin, Maacah le asepai te jong ana kitho piu ve. Chule hiche sepai ho chu Medaba mun a Hanun in amakhopi tah a anapan sah sepai ho toh chun ana umkhom uvin ahi.
\v 8 David in hichu ajah phat in Joab le asepai gal hang ho chu ama kisat pi din ana sol pai in ahi.
\v 9 Hichun Ammon mite jong ahung kon doh un khopi kelkot phung ah chun galsat dingin ahung kigol doh tauve, chule galsat dia hung kon leng ho jong chun ama hinathei cheh in galsat dia kigot na panmun akisem uvin ahi.
\v 10 Joab in amelmaten anung ama a ahin nokhum amu doh phat in Israel te sepai hatlai ho chu Aramean sepai te kisat pi dingin alhengdoh in ahi.
\v 11 Chule aman sepai dang adalhah chengse chu asopipa Abishai lamkai nanoi a Ammon mite kisat pi dingin apan sah e.
\v 12 Joab in asopipa jah a chun, “Aramean mite chu kahin jolal le neihung kithopi ding chule nangin jong Ammon mite nanjolal le kahung kithopi ding nahi,” ati.
\v 13 Hat unlang hangsan tah in pang un e Pathen khopi ule emiteu va dingin gal isat diu ahi. Pakaiyin ama deilam in hinbol jeng tahen.
\v 14 Joab le asepaiten Aramean mite àsat un anadel jam tauve.
\v 15 Chule Ammon miten Aramean mite jam amu doh phat u chun Abishai a kon'in anajam un akhopiuva ana kile tauve.
\v 16 Aramean miten Israel te ajolel u ahetdoh phat uchun Euphrates luipang le avel dung a kon'in Aramean sepaite akoukhom in amaho chu abon'un Hadadezer sepai jalamkai pa thunoi in ana um sah uvin ahi.
\v 17 David in hitobng thilumchan ho ahet doh phat in jordan vadung vel dung a kon jousea Israel sepaite chu galsat din ana kou khom in Aramean mite toh ana kisat tauvin ahi.
\v 18 Chule Aramean mite chu Israel te a kon'in anagal lel un, anajam kit tauvin ahi. Hichea chun David sepai ten Aramean sepai lamkai pipu Shobah pum in sepai kangtalai tol mi sang sagi le kenglam sepai mi sang somli jen ana that uvin ahi.
\v 19 Hadadezer thunoi a leng umhon jong Israel ten gal ajo amudoh phat uvin, David angsung a akipelut uvin ama thunoi in aum tauve, chule Aramean miten a-itih a jong Ammon mite akitho pi kit diu anom tapouve.
\c 20
\s1 David In Rabbah Ajo
\p 
\v 1 Chuche kum chavang lai a lengpa galbol dia ahung chun Israel mite chun Job lamkai na noi in Ammon mite anasat uvin ahi. Hichun aman Rabbah khopi chu ana umkhom in ahi. Hinlah David chu Jerusalem ah chun ana umden in ahi. \x + \xo 20:1 \xt 2 Samuel 11:1\x*
\v 2 David Rabbah khopi ahung lhun in lengpa lallukhuh chu aladoh in aman akikhuh in ahi. Hiche lal lukhuh chu sana pah jem a kisem chule agih dan jong pound som sagi le nga ahi. David in jong thilman tampi khopia chun ahin kipoh in ahi.
\v 3 Aman Rabbah kho mite chu soh in ana mang in, amaho chu thingat, thih khenchi a leilai le heicha’a thing chan in anapan sah in, Ammon mite chu engbolna ana pen ahi. Chujouvin David le asepaite chu Jerusalem a anache tauve.
\s1 David In Philistine Chunga Galojana Anei
\p 
\v 4 Chujouvin jong Israel te le Philistine te chu Gazer mun a gal in ana kisat kit in ahi. Hiche akisat nau va hin, Hushah kho a Sebbecai jin milen galhat minthang ho chilhah a kon Saph kitipa ana that in chule Philistine ten gal ana lel tauvin ahi.
\v 5 Philistine te toh gal kisat na mun khat ma ana um kit in, hichea chun Elhanan chapa Jair chun Gath khoa kon Goliath sopipa Lahmi chu anathat in ahi. Chule Lahmi tenglum chu lentah ahi. \x + \xo 20:5 \xt 1 Samuel 17:4-7\x*
\v 6 Philistine tetoh Gath khopia gal ana kisat namun uva jong chun milentah galhat mi khut jung gup le keng jung gup nei abon'a somni le li nei khat ana pang e, ama hi gollui lai galhang minthang ho son chilhah a kon ahi.
\v 7 Chule aman Israel mite totnop na le noise tah a anabol jeh chun David sopipa Shimea chapa Jonathan in’a anathat tai.
\v 8 David in anatha Philistine galhang mite hi Gath kho akon milui galhang ho son chilhah jeng anahiu ve.
\c 21
\s1 David, Satan In Apatep Chule Mijat Asimtoh
\p 
\v 1 Israel douna din, Satan’in Israel chate mijat simdin David lengpa atildoh tai.
\v 2 Hijeh hin David nin Joab le a sepai lamkai ho jah ah, “Sahlam gamkai Bersheba apat lhumlam gamkai Dan chan gei Israel mijat gasim uvin lang, nasimdoh jat u chu kaheng’a hinchoi’un, keiman kahet nom’e.
\v 3 Ahin Joab’in adonbut’in, “Pakaiyin Israel chate ajat ja’n hin punsah hen. Ahin ka Pakai le ka Lengpa, amaho khu namite hilou ham? Iding’a ka Pakaipa’n hiche nabol nom ham? Iding’a Israel te chung’a themmona lhunsah ding nagot ham?” ati.
\v 4 Ahivang’in, lengpan athusei chu apetchah in, hijeh chun Joab jong lengpa thupeh nit’in Israel chate chenna gam jousea mijat agasim in Jerusalem ahung kile tai.
\v 5 Hichun ajatsimdoh jat chu David heng’a ahetsah tai. Gaalhang chemjam lamthei cheh chu mi nel khat le sang jakhat alhingin, Judah mite jong Sang jali le sang somsagi alhing uve.
\v 6 Hiche jatsim ahin Joab in Levi mite le Benjamin mite vang asimtha pon ahi ajeh chu, lengpa thupeh chu Joab in ama boldia adeimo behseh jeng ahi.
\v 7 Hichun, Pathen'in mijatsim kibolchu alunghanpi jeh in ami Israel te chu gotna achantan ahi.
\v 8 Chuphat’in David in Pathen jah a hitin aseitai, “Vo Kapathen, keiman nangma doumahtah kaboldoh tai, ngol-hoitah hijongleh neingaidam kit in,” ati.
\v 9 Chuphatchun, Pathen'in David ding’a mitva neiya pangpa Gad heng’a hitin aseitai,
\v 10 “David heng’a gache’n lang Pathen'in hitin aseiye tin gaseipeh tan”, gimbolna thum lah a hin khat kilhen inlang, hichu keiman ka guilhun sah tei ding ahi”, ati.
\v 11 Hijeh chun David heng’a Gad ahung’in hitin aseitai, “Pathen'in hicheng thum hi nagon pehtai,”
\v 12 “Kum thum sung’a kellhah ding nadei’am, na galmiten chemjam a lhathum sungsea nasuhgam ding nalhen ding ham ahilou le, ni thum sung a gamna hise nasatah a lhung’a na lenggam sung pumpia pakai vantil in namite asuhgam ding hoichi nalhen joh ding ham?” “Eihin solpa Pathen heng’a iti kalhut ding nalhen joh hitam?” ati.
\v 13 “Kadinmun ahahsa valtai” tin David in Gad jah a aseitai. “iti nama jongleh mihem khut a kipeh sang’in Ka Pakai, Ka Pathen khut joh’in kipelut tang’e. Ajeh chu, amihepina kidangtahchu kakinem nalaiye” ati.
\v 14 Hichun, Pathen'in Israel te lah a gamna hise alansah tan, mi sangsom sagi jen in thina atoh tai.
\v 15 Chuban’a jong, Pathen'in Jerusalem sugamhel din mithat vantil ahinsoltan ahileh, akigotjinglai un, Pathen'in alung ahin heiyin, vantil jah a, “Aphaset tai, ngatan” tin aseitai. Chupet tah chun, mithat vantil chu Jerusalem chungvum’a ana pansa tan ahi. Hichu Jebus mipa Araunah changphol ahitai.
\v 16 David in vanlang a Pakai vantil ten chemjam pum a Jerusalem suhgam ding agot u amu phat’in. Israel lamkai pipuho toh kisih pumin tol lang ngan, khaodip ponsil pum’in.
\v 17 Chuin, David in Pathen jah a aseitai, “Israel te mijatsim ding’a thupeh nei chu keima kahi, abolkhel le achonse chu keima kahi, kamite vang kelngoi bang’a themmona ipi aboldoh u hitam? O ka Pakai le ka Pathen’u, nalunghanna kei le ka insung mite chung’a chuhsah tan, namite vang sugam hih hel in.
\v 18 Hichun, Pakai vantil’in Gad jah a David achetou a Jebus mipa Araunah changphol a maichamphung asah din thupeh aneitai.
\v 19 Hijeh chun David in Gad thulhut bangin Pathen thupeh chu boldin achetou tai.
\v 20 Araunah le achapa te mi li chun suhlou chang ana den pettah in Vantil chu amu uvin ahileh, achapa te chu akichat jeh un ajam uvin akisel gam taove.
\v 21 Araunah in David chu changphol ahinphah amu phat’in, a bolban dalhan Lengpa chu ana bohkhup tai.
\v 22 David in Araunah jah a hitin aseitai, “Na Changphol mun hi aman lhingsel keiman nape’ng ting, Pakai maicham phungkhat satang’e, chuteng Pakai lunghan na hiche gimna hise jong thip tante”.
\v 23 “Kilah inlang nadei bangtah in mangcha tan Kapu, chujongleh keiman Pumgo thilto a manchah din Bongchalte, maicham mei ti nadin changsuh thing chule, thilto din suhlou chang jong pehtha nge” tin Araunah in David jah a aseitai.
\v 24 Ahivangin Leng David in Araunah adonbut in, “keiman aman lhingset napeng ting, nangma thil vang maicham thilto din kilah tha pong’e”.
\v 25 Chuin, David in Araunah chu sana pheng jagup chu changphol man dingin apetai.
\v 26 Hilaimun hin David in maicham phungkhat asan, pumgo thilto le kichamna maicham asemin, taona amang tan ahile, Pathen'in asanpeh hetna din van'a kon meikou ahin sol lhan pumgo thilto jouse akavam hel tai.
\v 27 Hijeh chun Pathen'in Chemjam ana lam’a kigo vantil chu a chempai a anungkoi din thu ape tai.
\v 28 Pathen'in amaicham sem asanpeh ahet phat’in David in jong Araunah changphol mun chun kilhaina maicham asemtai.
\v 29 Hiche phat laiya hi, Pakai Houbuh maicham le pumgo thilto maicham phung, Mose in gammang laiya anasem chu Gibeon mun a aumpet ahi.
\v 30 Ahivangin David chun hiche laimun a chu Pathen lung gahol a gache ding chu agel le mithat vantil chemjam toh gotsa dem a anaum jeh chun angapcha pon ahi.
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 Chuin David in aseitai, “Hilai mun hi Pathen Hou-In mun chu hi ding ahitai, chule kilhaina, pumgo thilto namun jong hi ding ahi.”
\s1 Hou-In Sahdohna Dinga David Kiging Pan
\p 
\v 2 Hijeh chun Leng David in gamsung a kholjin mijouse akoutup in, aboltheina cheh un Hou-In sah nading song khengjol loi apansah tai.
\v 3 David in Kelkot a man ding thingkil semna din thih tampi leh sum eng te khopset apen ahi.
\v 4 Tyre le Sidon miten Leng David ana peh Cedar thingtum ho jongchu tampi ana peh thai.
\v 5 David in aseitai, “Kachapa Solomon hi achapang nalaiyin, jilna le hetna jong neibeh nailou hijongleh, Pathen'in anganse a Hou-In sahdoh ding hi loupi ding, minthang ding chuleh leiset pumpia dia jong nasatah hi ding ahin, hijeh a chu tua hi kagonpeh pan ding ahitai.” Hijeh a hi David in athi masang a Hou-In sah nadia thil le lo tampi akoitup ahitai.
\v 6 Hichun, David in achapa Solomon jah a Israel te Pathen chenna ding Hou-In theng asahdoh natei din athumop tai.
\v 7 “Kachapa, keiman ka Pathen jabol nadin a Hou-In theng khat kasadoh nom’e.” David in aseipeh in, \x + \xo 22:7 \xt 2 Samuel 7:1-16; 1 Thusimbu 17:1-14\x*
\v 8 “Ahivangin Pathen'in kajah a aseiye, nangman nagalbolna munna mi tampi nathat tan”. “Chuleh, keima mitmua thisan tampi naso tah jeh a, nangman keima jabol nadia ka Hou-In theng nasah theilou ding ahitai”.
\v 9 “Ahivang’a, Chamnasem chapa khat nahin ding ahi, aman Lengvai apoh sungsea Israel gam leh akimvel a agalmite kisan geiya chamdel a kalhat sah ding ahi. Amin Solomon kiti ding chuleh ama lengvai poh sung’a hi Israel cham kalensah ding ahi.”
\v 10 “Ama hi ahi keima jabol nadia Hou-In theng sadoh ding chu. Kachapa deitah hintin, keima apa kahi ding ahi. Chuleh keiman a itih a alenggam sung’a chamna le lungmon konna kapeh ding ahi.”
\v 11 Kacha tuhin, Pakaiyin nakithopi intin; aman nangma chung chang thudol’a asei tobangin, nangman jong Pakai, Pathen Hou-In nahinsah doh tei ding ahi.
\v 12 Pakajin thil hetkhen themna le datkhenji dan napeh ding, Israel chunga vaihom a natun ding, ngansena nahin peh teng jongleh Pakai, na Pathen danthu nanit jingna dingin nabol peh tahen.
\v 13 Israel te dinga Pakaiyin Mose athupeh chonna dan ahin, chondan jouse chu nanit jing ding chule ching thei tah’a nakhan toupi thei ding ahi. Hijeh chun hat inlang, hang in, kicha hih hel in chule lungthoina jong nanei louding ahi. \x + \xo 22:13 \xt Joshua 1:6-9\x*
\v 14 Genthei hesohna tothon keiman Pakai Hou-In sahdohna dingin, sana talent sang jakhat kakhol khom in ahi. Chule dangka talent nelkhat jong kakhol khom in, sum eng le thih jong ajat’a tekham valset kakhol khom e, ijeh-inem itileh atam in, in thil le lo jong kakhol khom sohkeijin, hiche ho jouse hi nangman nabolbe ding ahina laiye.
\v 15 Natong ding mihem tampi semdoh in: song kheng them miho, thing thembol miho, thing vaibol miho, aloi loija mihem simjou lou mihem khutthemna neiho nakoi ding, khut themna neitah beh,
\v 16 mi sana lha-them, dangka kheng them, sum-eng lha them, thih kheng them chule adang mitampi nakoi ding ahi. Tun kipat in na-tong tan, Pakaiyin napanpi jing tahen! ati.
\v 17 Chuin David in Israel mite sunga lamkai chengse thupeh aneiyin, achapa Solomon akithopi diuvin thu aseijin ahi.
\v 18 “Pakai, na Pathen uvin nangho napanpi jingo hilou ham? Ama tah in na jet le naveiju hungkon nagal miteu asuh thip’a chamna naneiju hilou ham? Ajeh chu Pakai, ama tah in agamsunga cheng mite chu keima khut’a apedoh in, hijeh chun agamsung jouse hi Pakai ansung leh amite masanga suh-nem’a uma, mite noija kikunsah ahitai.
\v 19 Tun nang hon na lungthim pumpiu Pakai, na Pathen-u hol tauvin. Kipat un Pakai, Pathen muntheng Hou-In satauvin; chutileh Pakai kitepna thingkong le Pathen Hou-In a manchah bel le um chule thilkeo atheng jouse hiche Pakai dinga Hou-In kisadoh sunga chu pohlut’a um ding ahitai,” ati.
\c 23
\s1 David In Houbuh Natong Dinga Levi te Akhop
\p 
\v 1 Chuin David ahung teh in, akum atamphat in achapa Solomon chu Isrealte lengpan apansah tai \x + \xo 23:1 \xt 1 Lgt 1:1-40\x*
\v 2 Aman Isreal gam a lengte, thempuho chule Levi mite akhom in ahi
\v 3 Levi te chu kum somthum apat chunglam se chu khat khat in akisim un, pasal mi sangsom thumle get alhing ui.
\v 4 Hinlah mi sang somni le sang li chu Pathen Hou-In sunga naa atoh sah in, chule mi sang gup chu alamkai le thutan vaihom dingin apansah tai.
\v 5 Chukitle mi sangli chu kot ngah din akoi in, mi sangli ma chu aman apeh tumging ho mangchan Pathen vahchoi jing dingin umhen tin David in aseije.
\v 6 Chuin David chu Levi chate Gershon, kohath le Merari min'in akhen kit in ahi.
\v 7 Gershon mite ho chu Laaadan le Shimei ahi
\v 8 Laadan chate chu Jehiel le Zatham le Joel agom a thum
\v 9 Shimei chate chu Shelomith leh Heziel le Haran ahi. Amaho hi Laadan insunga mi upaho ahiuve
\v 10 Chule Shimei chate chu Jahath, Ziza, Zeush chule Beriah. Amaho li hi Shimei chate ahiuve.
\v 11 Chule Jahath chu Haosa lamkai ana hin, Zizah chu ani channa anahi, amavang Jeush chule Beriah teni hin chapa tampi ana hing lhon lou jeh in pakhat insung in akisim tai.
\v 12 Kohath hin chapa li ana hingin amaho chu; Amran, Izahar, Hebron chule Uzziel anahiuve.
\v 13 Amaram cha Pasal teni chu Aaron chule Mose ana hi. Aaron hin Pathen a dingin pumgo thilto ana lhantheng jing theinadia chule ama achapa ten atonsot a Pathen anga thilto gimnamtui ana hal jing uva; ama lenggam a dinga akipehdoh jing uva, chule ama minna phatthei achan jing theina diuvin, asopipa toh ana ki sukhen in ahi. \x + \xo 23:13 \xt Potdohbu 28:1\x*
\v 14 Mose hi Pathen mipan ana kisim in ahi. Achapa te chu Levi chilhah noiya ana ki minvon ahi.
\v 15 Mose chapa te chu Gershom chule Eleizer ana hi hone.
\v 16 Gershom chapa telah a chun Shebul chu ana haosa lamkaiyin ahi,
\v 17 Chule Eleizer chapa te lah a Rehabiah chu ana Haosa lamkaiyin ahi. Eleizer hin chapa dang ana hingpon ahi, amavang Rehabia hin chapa tampi ana hing in ahi.
\v 18 Izhar chapa te lah a Shalomith chu ana haosa lamkaiyin ahi.
\v 19 Hebron chapa te lah a Jeriah chu ana tah pen in ahi, Amariah chu anina an hin, Jahaziel chu athumna chule Jekameam chu ali channa ana hi.
\v 20 Uzziel chapa te lah a Micah chu atahpen in chule Issiah chu ani channa ana hi.
\s1 Merari Chilhah Te
\p 
\v 21 Merari Chate ho chu Mahli le Mushi ahin Mahli chapa te chu Mahli, Eleazer le Kish ahiuve.
\v 22 Chapa nei louva Eleazar thi chule chanu bou aneiyin ahi. Chule asopi Kish chapa ten achanu te akichen pin ahi.
\v 23 Mushi Chate ho chu Athum uvin- Mahli, Eder chule Jeremoth ho ahiuve
\v 24 Hichengse hi Levi insungmi le ason apah ho chengse ahiuve- amin kikhumlut dungjuijin insung lamkai ho chengse jong achangseh'in akisim in ahi
\v 25 Chuin David in, Isreal Pathen chun amite cholngah sah in chule atonsot a Jerusalem a cheng ding ahi.
\v 26 Pathen Houbuh a kimang le athil ho chengse jong Levi ten anungpoh kit lou diu ahitai. \x + \xo 23:26 \xt Danbu Ni Na 10:8\x*
\v 27 David hilchah na achainapen dungjuijin, Levi te chu kum somni a tah le achunglam apat kisim pan ahi.
\v 28 Levi te chun Pathen Houbuh a Aaron chapa te akithopiuva, indan ho sutheng le ding, thil thengho koitup ding chule Pathen Houbuh a natoh chengse vetup ding ahiuve. \x + \xo 23:28 \xt Minbu 3:5-9\x*
\v 29 Dokhanga changlhah luidoh ding, todoh ding changbong ho chule ajat alet aneo dungjui a haltoh ding chengse jong avettup diu ahi.
\v 30 Jingkah seh le ding uva Pathen a vahchoi dingu ahi. Nilhah le angaima banga abol kit diu ahi.
\v 31 Chule ama hon Sabbath nikho le Lhathah nikho a Pakai anga thilto abol teng ule amijat ana ngaichat dungjui a abol diu ahi.
\v 32 Hiti chun Levi ten ten ponbuh a kinbol hihen muntheng kibol hihen, asopiu Aaron chapa te chu Pakai kibol na’a akithopi jing diu ahi.
\c 24
\p 
\v 1 Aaron chapa te kihop khen dan chu hiti hi ahi: Nadab ahin, Abihu ahin, Eleazer leh Ethamar amaho cheng hi ahiuve.
\v 2 Nadab le Abihu hi apa sang'in athimasa lhonin, chajong aneiman lhon tapoi; chuin Eleazer leh Ithamar chu thempu ahung hilhon tai. \x + \xo 24:2 \xt Thempu Dan 10:1,2\x*
\v 3 Eleazar chapa te lah a kon’le Zadok le Ithamar chapa te lah a kon Ahimelech panpina jal’in David chun ama ama natoh ding toh kisaijin agoltoh sohkeijun ahi.
\v 4 Ithamar chapa te sang'in, Eleazar chapa te sunga chun miupa atam un, hijeh chun Eleazar chapa te lah a chun apu apateu insung lhahdol cheh in, lamkai somle gup alhengdoh un, amaho lamkai nan aum un ahi. Chule Ithamar chapte dingin lamkai miget bou ana lhengdoh un ahi.
\v 5 Akilhengdoh le lamkaija kipansah ho hi kibang chetna vang kisansah ahiuvin, hitia akibolnaa kon chun Eleazar leh Ithamar chapa te lah a kon'in, muntheng a natong vaihom ding leh Pathen natohna vaibol ding tampi kisepdoh ahi.
\v 6 Nathanel kiti Levi mi Shemiah hi danthu them ahin, amaho chengse chu lengpa le milen milalte angsung, Zadok thempupa angsung le Abiathar chapa Ahimelech angsung le thempu ho chule Levi miho, apu apateuva pat phung upa chengse lekha in ajihlut tan ahi; ajeh chu pa khang khat lhahse chu Eleazar insunga kon kilhengdoh ahin, chule pa khang khat lhah chengse ma chu Ithamar insunga dia kilhengdoh ahi.
\v 7 Vang kisan masapen chu Jehoiarib chunga achun, chuin ani na chu Jedaiah chunga achun,
\v 8 athumna chu Harim chunga achun; alina chu Seorim chunga achun,
\v 9 angana chu Malchijah chunga achun, agupna Mijamin chunga achun,
\v 10 asagina chu Hakkoz chunga achun, agetna chu Abijah chunga achun,
\v 11 a konnan Jeshua chunga achun, asomna Shecaniah chunga achun,
\v 12 asom le khatna Eliashib chunga achun, asomle nina chu Jakim chunga achun,
\v 13 asomle thumna chu Huppah chunga achun, asomle li na chu Jeshebeab chunga achun,
\v 14 asomle nga na chu Bilgah chunga achun, asomle gup na chu Immer chunga achun,
\v 15 asom le sagi na chu Hezir chunga achun, asomle get na chu Happizzer chunga achun,
\v 16 asomle ko na chu Pethahiah chunga achun, somni na chu Jehezkel chunga achun,
\v 17 asomni le khat na chu Jachin chunga achun, asomni le ni na chu Gamul chunga achun,
\v 18 asomni le thumna chu Delaiah chunga achun, asomni le li nah cu Maaziah chunga achun ahi.
\v 19 Amaho chengse hi akipansahna cheh uvin, natoh ding anei cheh un, Pathen Hou-In sung ahung lut phat uleh, Pakai, Israel Pathen'in Apupau Aaron thu anapeh bang leh, Aaron in amaho chengse toh ding agontoh banginatohdiuva kilom cheng chu atong jiuvin ahi.
\v 20 Levi chapa te adangse chu: Amran chapa tea kon Shubael, chule Shubael chapa tea kon Jehdeiah ahi.
\v 21 Rehabiah chapa te chu: Rehabiah chapa tea kon Isshiah chu aupa pen ahi.
\v 22 Izhar chapa tea kon Shelomoth ahin, Shelomoth chapa tea kon Jahath ahi.
\v 23 Hebron chapa te chu: Jeriah chu aupapen ahin, ani channapa chu Amariah ahin, athum channapa chu Jahaziel ahin, ali channapa chu Jekameam ahi.
\v 24 Uzziel chapa tea kon Micah ahin, Micah chapa tea kon Shamir ahi.
\v 25 Micah sopipa chu Isshiah ahin, Isshiah chapa tea kon Zechariah ahi.
\v 26 Merari chapa te ni chu Jaaziah Mahli le Mushi ahilhon e. Jaaziah chapa tea kon Beno ahi.
\v 27 Merari chapa te chu Jaaziah chapa tea kon Beno le Shoham, Zaccur le Ibri ahiuve.
\v 28 Mahil chapa chu: Eleazar ahin, amapa hin chapa ana hing tapoi.
\v 29 Kish akon Kish chapa tea kon Jerahmeel ahi.
\v 30 Mushi chapa te chu Mahli le Eder chule Jerimoth ahiuve. Amaho chengse hi Levi mitea kon chapa, apu apateu lhah’a ama insung cheh’a kon kisimdoh ahiuve.
\v 31 Amaho chengse hin apa jang lhah insung cheh in, asopi teu umchan banginAaron chapa te nunle khan athouvin ahi. David lengpa angsung le Zadok angsung, Ahimelech chule thempu ho apu apateu insung cheh’a kon chule Levi miho masanga chun vang akisan cheh tauve.
\c 25
\s1 Pakai Lhendoh Lathem Ho
\p 
\v 1 David le a sepai jalamkaiten Asaph, Heman chule Jeduthun insungmi chu Kipana Thupha sapphong toh thoa semjang gin ngei, tumging chule Khutbeh la lamkai din alhengdoh taove.
\v 2 Asaph chapa te Zaccur, Joseph, Nethaniah chule Asarelah in jong a pau maikainan lengpa thupeh dungjuijin Kipana Thupha chu alhangsap uve.
\v 3 Heduthun chapa te, Gedaliah, Zeri, Jeshiah, Shimei, Hashabiah chule Mattithah mi gup cheng hin jong a pau makainan semjang gin ngei, thangvah le vahchoi toh thon Kipana Thupha sapphong toh thon Pathen athangvah uve.
\v 4 Heman chapa te chu Bukkiah, Mattaniah, Hanani, Eliathah, Giddalti, Romam’ti-e’zer, Joshbekashah, Mallothi, Hothir chule Mahazioth cheng hi ahiuve.
\v 5 Lengpa Themgao a pang Heman hin Pakaiya a kon'in chapa Somle li le chanu thum ahing e.
\v 6 Heman le achapa te chu Hou-In sunga tumging thei, Selangdah gin ngei, Semjang sai chule khutbeh a Pakai vahchoina lamkaiya pang ahiuve. Chule ijakaiyin, Asaph, Jeduthun chule Heman jong lengpa toh aki thukop jing uve.
\v 7 Amaho insung hi Pakai vahchoi na mun a tumging sai ding mong a hung kitillu ahi. Abonchauvin tumging sai thei cheh mi Jani somget le get alhing uve.
\v 8 Mi hichengse hi teh le khang hihen jilkung le simlai umlouvin athepna cheh uva apang un chuleh vang kibanginakisan cheh uve.
\v 9 Mi jani somget le get ho hin, chapa somle ni cheh in asauvin, hichengse ho hi hopsomni le li in aki homson uvin asopite cheng to vang akisan uve.Vang kisan masapen chu Asaph chilhah lah a Joseph le asopite ahiuvin. Anina a vang kisan chu Gedaliah le asopite ahi,
\v 10 athum channa Zaccur,
\v 11 ali channa Zeri,
\v 12 a nga channa Nethaniah,
\v 13 a gup channa Bukkiah,
\v 14 a sagi channa Asarelahz,
\v 15 a get channa Jessiah,
\v 16 a ko channa Mattaniah,
\v 17 a som channa Shimei,
\v 18 a somle khat na Uzziel,
\v 19 a somle ni na Hashabiah,
\v 20 a somle thumna Shubael,
\v 21 a somle li na Mattithiah,
\v 22 a somle nga na Jerimoth,
\v 23 a somle gup na Hannaniah,
\v 24 a somle sagi na Joshbekashah,
\v 25 a somle get na Hanani,
\v 26 a somle ko na Mallothi,
\v 27 a somni na Eliathah,
\v 28 a somni le khat na Hothir,
\v 29 a somni le ni na Giddalti,
\v 30 a somni le thumna Mahazioth,
\v 31 a somni le li na Romamti-ezer.
\c 26
\s1 Kelkotbul Ngah Ho Chung Chang
\p 
\v 1 Kelkotbul ngah ho kivaihop dan chu hiti ahi: Korah chilhah a konna Kore chapa Meshelemiah kitipa hi Abiasaph insung a kon ahi.
\v 2 Meshelemiah in chapa sagi ahin chu atahpen Zechariah ahin, abanna Jediael, Zebadiah, Jathniel,
\v 3 Elam, Jehohanan chuleh Eliehoenai ahiuve.
\v 4 Kelkot ngahpa Obed-edom chu Pathen'in chapa get jenin phattheina dimset aboh in, amaho cheng chu atahpen Shemaiah, Jehozabad, Joah, Sacar, Nethanel, \x + \xo 26:4 \xt 2 Samuel 6:11; 1 Thusimbu 13:14\x*
\v 5 Ammiel, Issachar chule Peullethai ahiuve.
\v 6 Obed-edom chapa Shemaiah chun chapa miboltheicheh ahing’in a phungsung u vaihom na a panmun nasatah alo cheh uve.
\v 7 Amaho chengse chu ahile, Othni, Rephael, Obed chule Elzabad ahiuve. Chubanle, asopi teniu Elihu le Semakiah jongchu miboltheitah ma ahi lhon e.
\v 8 Obed-edom chilhah, achapa te le a tute mi somgup le ni chengse hi natohna a feltah le bolthei cheh ahiuve.
\v 9 Meshelemiah chapa te mi somle get le asopite chengse hi miboltheitah ahicheh uve.
\v 10 Merari phungsung a kon'in Hosah chun Shimri chu achapa te lah a atahpen ahilouvangin lamkai din alhengdoh tai.
\v 11 Achapa te chu aninapa Hilkiah, Tebaliah, Zechariah jong ahiuvin. Hosah chapa te le asopite mi somle thum chengse chu kelkot ngah in apang uve.
\v 12 Hitobanga kelkot ngah ho kivaihop danhi Levi dang ho banga a insungmi cheh in Pakai na chu atoh u ahi.
\v 13 Kelkot ngah dia kelkot tin a insungmiten ahin deilhen hi kumle lha hihen, theple theplou man a kive hilouin a vang kisan dungjui a pang ji ahiuve.
\v 14 Solam kelkot ngah a pang din Meshelemiah le aloite nganse ahitauvin, sahlam chu michingtah a kihepa Zechariah,
\v 15 Lhanglam kelkot chu Obed-edom nganse ahin, achapa te chu thil kholna kelkot ngah in apang uve.
\v 16 Shuppim le Hosah chu lhumlam kelkot apat a Shallecheth kelkot chan gei ngah din lamkai a apang lhonin, anga pi ho chu akimaingat sah in limgeh in apang uve.
\v 17 Solam kelkot phung chun niseh in mi gup, sahlam a mi li, lhanglam a mi li ma chuleh mi li kingato cheh in thil kholna kelkot phungin apang jing’ui.
\v 18 Lhumlam kelkot phunga mi gup chuleh mi li chu kotpi a kon a Shallecheth chan apang un, mini ma avel lah chun apang’e.
\v 19 Korah le Merari phungsung a kelkot ngah ho kivaihopdan hiti chu ahi.
\s1 Hou-In Sunglam Kivaihomdol
\p 
\v 20 Ahijah lamkainan maicham thil kholna mun le Hou-In gou ho khol namun avetup uve.
\v 21 Gershon phungkhai, Libni insung’a kon'in Jehiel chu lamkai khat in apang’e.
\v 22 Jehiel, Zetham chule Joel chapa te jong Pathen maicham thil kholna mun chu ngah din nganse na achang taove.
\v 23 Hiche lamkai a pang cheng hi Amram, Izhar, Hebron chuleh Uzziel chilhah ahiuve.
\v 24 Amram phungsung a dia, Shebuel chu Mose chapa, Gershom chilhah ahin.
\s1 Ama Hi Thilkhol Na A Vaibol Pipu Ahi.
\p 
\v 25 Asopite Eliezer in ahin ho chu, Rehabiah, Jeshaiah, Joram, Zocri chule Shelomoth ahiuve.
\v 26 Shelomoth le asopite hi Leng David, insung lamkai pipu, sepai jalamkai chuleh mi thupi hon Pakaiya dia maicham thilto a ahin peh hou anga u ahi.
\v 27 Galmun a kon a kichomkhom thilhoi lai2 ho jong Pakai Hou-In sunga manchah le din ahin lhandoh jiuve.
\v 28 Chujongleh, Shelomoth le asopi ten Themgao Samuel, kish chapa Saul, Ner chapa Abner le Zeruiah chapa Joab thilto ho jong achingtup jing uve.
\s1 Levi te Panlah Dan
\p 
\v 29 Izhar phung a kon'in Kenaniah ahung pengdoh in, a chapa te toh Israel sung a vaibol le thutan in apang uve.
\v 30 Hebron phung a kon'in Hashabiah ahung pengdoh in, asopite thil bolthei cheh sang le ja sagi toh Jordan vadung a patna lhumlam a um Israel te gambeh sunga, Pathen thulam hihen lang Lenggam thu hijongleh nganse na lentah achang taove.
\v 31 Chujongleh, Hebron phung a kon'in Jeriah ahung pengdoh in, ama hi Hebronte phunggui kisut dan a lamkai le khat anahi. David lengpa kum somli alhin a akhouldoh dungjui uva, Hebron te lah a mibolthei tampi Gilead gam Jazer khopi a amudoh u ahi.
\v 32 Miboltheitah mi ho chu mi sangni le ja sagi chengse chu Jeriah sopite ngen jeng ahiuve. Amaho hi Leng David in Jordan vadung a pat a solam a asol a Reuben leh Gad chule Mannaseh chilhah akehkhat langpi vekol ding a ejakai a Pathen thulam hihen, Lenggam thu hijongleh nganse na lhingset chang ahiuve.
\c 27
\s1 David Lengvaipohna Sunga Vaibol Ho
\p 
\v 1 Israel sepai jalamkaite le a vaibol teuvin lengpa hongbit dia a sepaite ahon hon a aki vaihop dan u chu hiti ahi. Sepai hon khat a mi sangsomni le li alhing uvin, kum khat le lhakhat cheh pan ala teiyun ahi.
\v 2 Sepai hon ho panmun la masapen a lamkai chu Zabdiel chapa Jashobeam ahi,
\v 3 Ama hi Perez insung a kon sepai vaihom ho jouse lah a jong thaneipen ahi.
\v 4 Sepaihon lhanina a pan la a lamkai chu Ahoah insungmi Dodai kitipa ahin, anoidou a thanei vaihom din Mikloth kitipa akikoi e.
\v 5 A lhathum channa a pan la sepaihon lamkai chu Jehoiada chapa Benaiah ahi.
\v 6 Beniah kitipa hi David sepai hangsan, mihat somthum ho lamkai a jong ana pang ahi. Achapa Ammizabad chu anoidou din apansah e.
\v 7 Joab naopa Asahel in a lhali channa sepai hon te alamkaiyin ahi. Ama hi achapa Zebadiah in athijouin apanmun akhel tai.
\v 8 A lhanga channa sepaihon lamkai chu Shammah ahin, ama hi Izrahite tinjong aki hei.
\v 9 A lhagup channa din Tekoa vangkhoa kon, Ikkesh chapa Ira chu lamkai in apang’e.
\v 10 A lhasagi channan Pelon akon a Ephraim insungmi Helez a lamkai e.
\v 11 A lhaget channan Hushah a kon Zerah insungmi Sibbecai a lamkaiyin.
\v 12 A lhako channan Benjamin gamsung, Anathoth a kon Abiezer a lamkai in.
\v 13 A lhasom nan Netophah a kon Zerah insungmi Maharai in a lamkaiye.
\v 14 A lhasom le khat nan Epharaim, Pirathon a kon Benaiah a lamkaiyin.
\v 15 A lhasom le ni na in Netophah a kon Othniel insungmi Heled in a lamkaiye.
\s1 Israel Phung Lamkaiho
\p 
\v 16 Reuben phung lamkai chu Zicri, Eliezer chapa ahi. Simeon phung lamkai chu Maacah chapa, Shephatiah ahi.
\v 17 Levi Phung lamkai, Kemuel chapa Hashabiah ahin, Aaron themgaote phung lamkai chu Zadok ahi.
\v 18 Judah te lamkai chu David sopipa Elihu ahin, Issachar lamkai chu Michael chapa Omri ahi.
\v 19 Zebulun lamkai in Obadiah chapa Ishmaiah apangin, Naphtali lamkai chu Azriel chapa Jeremoth ahi.
\v 20 Ephraim Phung lamkai chu Azaziah chapa Hoshea ahin, Lhumlam Manasseh lamkai chu Pedaiah chapa Joel ahi.
\v 21 Solam Gilead a Manasseh lamkai chu Zechariah chapa Iddo ahi. Benjamin lamkai a Abner chapa Jaasiel apang in.
\v 22 Dan lamkaiyin Jeroham chapa Azarel apang’e.
\v 23 Leng David in mijatsim abolna achun kum somni a pat anoilam ho asimtha pon ahi. Ajeh chu, Pathen'in Israel chate chu van'a ahsi jat a phatthei aboh dia akitepna akoisa ahitai. \x + \xo 27:23 \xt Semtilbu 15:5; 22:17; 26:4\x*
\v 24 Zeruiah chapa Joab chun mijatsim ijat a aboldoh kigot vang'in alosap jing’e. Ajeh chu Pathen lunghan na chang a, Leng David khang a Israel mijatsim chu lolhing lou ahitai. \x + \xo 27:24 \xt 2 Samuel 24:15; 1 Thusimbu 21:1-14\x*
\v 25 Adiel chapa Azmaveth chu lengpa thil kholna ngahtup din nganse ahin, Uzziah chapa Jonathan chu khopi thil kholna mun jouse ngahtup din nganse ahitai.
\v 26 Kelub chapa Ezri chun Lengpa loubol ho vetup din Loumun angah in,
\v 27 Ramah a kon Shimei chu Lengpa lengpi lei ngahtup in apang in, Sepham a kon Zabdi chu Lengpa Ju le Lengpitwi thah a apang’e.
\v 28 Geder a kon a Baal-Hanan chun Judah te moul bul a um Lengpa Olive honsung chule theichang, theiba lei chu angahtup in ahi. Lengpa heng’a Olive thao thah jing din Joash ngansena achang’e.
\v 29 Sharon a kon Shitrai chu Sharon munjang lang’a Bong ching in apangin. Adlai chapa Shaphat chu phaicham lang’a apang e.
\v 30 Ishamel chilhah Obil in Sangong saote aching in. Meronoth a kon Jehdeiah in Sangaan aching e.
\v 31 Hagrite mi Jaziz in Lengpa kelngoi le kelcha aching in. Amaho chengse hi Lengpa gou ching jeng ahiuve.
\v 32 David pa-ngahpa Jonathan chu michingtah le thil hethei tah chule lengpa semang khat ahin. Hachmoni chapa Jehiel chu lengpa chapa jilkung in apang’e.
\v 33 Ahithophel kitipa hi Leng insung a thumop themtah ahin. Ark kho a Hushai kitipa hi Lengpa dia agol khat ahi.
\v 34 Benaiah leh Abiathar chapa Jehoiada in Ahithophel athi jouvin a panmun ahin khel in, Joab chu Lengpa sepai jalamkai a apangtai.
\c 28
\s1 Pathen Ding Un Tia David In Mipi Atilkhou
\p 
\v 1 David in alenggam sung’a sepai jalamkai, vaipo le vaibol jouse, phung lamkai hihen gou ching hihen, hetthei a panmun la jouse chuleh gaalhang jouse Jerusalem a akou sohkei un.
\v 2 Akipatdoh in hity hin aseitai, “Ka sopi le Ka mite ho, keiman Pathen kitepna thingkong a itih a aum jing nading, Pathen Hou-In theng sahdoh ding ka ngaiton, kigotnan thil le lo angaicha tampi jong kakoitai. \x + \xo 28:2 \xt 2 Samuel 7:1-16; 1 Thusimbu 17:1-14\x*
\v 3 Ahinlah, Pakai Pathen'in keima gaal-hat tah chuleh mi tampi that kahi jeh in eiphal pon ahi.
\v 4 Hijeng jongleh, Israel Pathen'in Judah te lah a konna, ka insung uva pat keimat ah, a itih hijongleh Israel leng dia ei thaonu ahitai.
\v 5 Chutah le, chapa tamtah phatthei eiboh ho lah a konna ka chapa Solomon in ka lengtou namun ei khel ding ahi” ati.
\v 6 Pathen'in kajah a aseiye, “Nachapa Solomon in Ka Hou-In theng le akimvel asahdoh dia kalhendoh ahitan, keiman angaichat ijakai kapeh jing ding ahi” ati.
\v 7 Chutah le, “Ka thupeh chengse anit jing’a ahile, Keiman a lenggam a itih a kaumpi jing ding ahi” ati.
\v 8 “Hijeh chun, Pakai le houbung pumpi angsung chuleh, Israel mite mitmun chingtheiyun lang na pakai na Pathen thupeh chengse nit jingun, chutileh lungmong a gampha lai na lo uva, nachateu le na tuteu khang geiya Pakai phattheina nachan jing diu ahi,” ati.
\v 9 “Chujongleh, Solomon kachapa, na Pu le na Pa phattheiboh jing na Pathen chu haimil lou jen’in. Nalungthim pumpin choi’an jinginlang athun um jingin, ajeh chu thil ijakai amun, ahe sohkeiyin, bel jing lechun, na lhaso louding ahi,” ati.
\v 10 “Hijeh chun, nalung gil in ngaiton. Pakai Pathen'in a Hou-In theng sa dia nalhendoh ahitan. Hat jingin lang natohdoh tei ding ahi,” ati.
\v 11 Chuin, David in athilgon ejakai, thil kholna indan ho chule chonset kingaidam na munho umdol jouse Solomon apetan ahi.
\v 12 David in alunggil a agontohsa, Hou-In lim asung apo, indan dang dang chule Maicham kibolna Muntheng dia agon ho jouse achapa Solomon aseipeh tai.
\v 13 Chujongleh, Hou-In sunga Themgao ho leh Levi mite panmun hihen, Pathen hou nadia thil le lo kimang ding jouse jong ahiltan ahi.
\v 14 David in Pathen Hou na a Sana le Sum eng man dia lom jat jong ahiltoh in,
\v 15 Solomon jah a Sana thaomei semna ding le sum eng thaomei semna ding chuleh sana le sum eng alut ding jat jong ahilthem in ahi.
\v 16 Changlhah hung kitohdoh ho koina ding Sana theng a kisem Dokhang chule, sum eng a kisem dokhang ho jong akisem na a sana angaicha ding jat jong ahilthem e.
\v 17 Thih-khe sana thengsel ijat a sem a, khon, Kong, Sil kong ho jouse sana ijat cheh a sem ding aboncha a atetoh peh soh e.
\v 18 Chujongleh, gimnamtui hal nading maicham phung semna dia sana thengsel man ding jat, chule Kangtalai sung a Cherubium vantil in a lhaving teni a akhu khum, Pakai kitepna thingkong sem ding dan jong ahiltan ahi.
\v 19 “Thilgon hichengse hi”, tin David in Solomon jah a, “Pathen'in akhut tah a asut eimudohsah akon kahet ahi” ati.
\v 20 David in abanjom in, “hat inlang hang jingin, natohdoh ding ahi. Kichat le lunglhah daina neihih hel in. Pakai Pathen'in na umpi jing’e. Nanganse nabang’a nachai theng tokah a Pakai Pathen'in na lhonpi jing ding ahi”.
\v 21 “Themgao ho le Levi mite akinganse na banga pakai kin abol diu, adangse injong akipeh nathei chan uva pan alah uva, gamsung vaipo ho jouse le thuneina aboncha a nangma thunoi a um ding ahi” ati.
\c 29
\s1 David In Mipi Ama Nungjui Pha Ahina Diuva Angeh
\p 
\v 1 Hichun, leng David in Hou-In sung’a mipi ho lam chu angan hitin aseiye, “Kachapa Solomon hi Pathen'in ka lengmun khel dia athaonusa chu ahin, ama chapang nalai intin, jilna neibeh nailou hijongleh, atoh dia lom Pathen'in angansena, a Hou-In sah dikhu mihem mai maiyin ajo chi vang ahipoi. \x + \xo 29:1 \xt 1 Thusimbu 22:5\x*
\v 2 Manchah theichan mangchan keiman ka Pathen Hou-In sah nadin sana, songmantam, thing le song ijakai angaicha jouse kakoitup peh tai. Hiho chu alhingset a dia, Sana, Sum eng, thih, thing chujongleh, Onyx tampi seh hilouin, Songmantam, Songval, Songpol, Marble song jong alhingset din kakoitup peh tai.
\v 3 Tunjong, keiman ka Pakaiya dia kakipehdoh nan ka Sana le sum eng jouse jong a Hou-In sah nadia kagotpeh ho ban’in kapedoh tai.
\v 4 Chuleh, keiman Hou-In bang dung ho sah nadin, Ophir a kon Sana talent jakhat som le ni chuleh, sum eng thengsel talent jani somgup le ni jong kapedoh tai.
\v 5 Chuban a, Khutthem ho tham ding Sana le Sum eng avat ding chengse ho hi, koi tobang ka Pakai ka Pathen a dia keijong kakipehdoh nom’e ti e um uvem?
\v 6 Hichun, mi upaho le Israel phung lamkai ho ahin, sepai jalamkaiho, gouching ho chuleh, lengpa vaibol ho jouse jong kiphaltheng tah in akipedohsoh taove.
\v 7 Pathen Hou-In theng sah nadia akipehdoh nao abonchauva apehdoh jat uchu, Sana talent jakhat somget le get, Dangka talent sangsom, sum eng talent jathum somsagi le nga, thih lhe talent jagup somsagi le nga chuleh, thih talent sangthum jasagi le somnga alhing’e.
\v 8 Chujongleh, Gershon chilhah a kon Jehiel in maicham thil kholna mun avetsui din anganse un, songmantam tampi jong atoh be cheh uve.
\v 9 Maicham thiltho ho jouse mipi ten hongphal tah le kiphaltheng tah a to jeh uvin akipah cheh uvin ahi. Chujongleh Lengpa David jong kipa leh thanop nan adim’e.
\s1 David, Pakai Vahchoina Le Taona
\p 
\v 10 Chuphat chun, Lengpa David in mipi jouse masang’in Pathen athangvah’e. “Kahung kondohnao Vo ka Pathen’u, atonsot tonsot'in nun nom in, namin kithangvah jinghen.
\v 11 Vo ka Pathen’u, minthanna jouse, loupi na jouse, thaneina jouse, jabol na jouse, ijakai nang’a hijing hen. Leiset pumpi le Vanthamjol abkonna nang’a ahi. Vo Kapathen’u thil ijakai nangma lenggam thaneina ahi. \x + \xo 29:11 \xt Matt 6:13\x*
\v 12 Houna le Jabolna nang’a kon bou ahi. Ajeh chu, imajouse nangma thunoi a umjeng ahi. Thaneina le loupina nangma khut a aum’in. Nangma khut’in minthanna le thaneina aboncha aum’e.
\v 13 Vo ka Pathen’u, namin thangvah le choi’ann na kahin peuve.
\v 14 Ahinlah, keima Koi kahiya, ka mite chu ipi hiuvam, nangma angsung a kipah le thanomtah a ipi hijongleh kapeh jing thei uham? Kanei, kagou jouseu nangma a konna kamu jeng u ahin, kapeh hou jouse nangman neipehsao ngen jeng ahi.
\v 15 Chuleh, kapu kapateu bang’a, Hiche leiset a hi khopem le maljin maimai kahiuvin, kahinkhou jong nilim kihei bang’in agei na akihepha ji tapoi.
\v 16 “Ka Pakai le ka Pathen’u, nangma jabol na, na Hou-In theng sah nadia kahin to khom u ijakai hi nang’a ahin, nangman neipeh jeng u ahi.
\v 17 Ka Pathen, nangman kalung’u nakholchilsoh jin, nalunglhai na chung’a nakipapi ji’e ti keima neihetsah in, chule lunggil tah a keiman thil hicheng kabol jong nahen ahi. Kamiten jong kipah le thanom tah thilto, thilpeh nangma Hou-In theng sahdoh nadia ahin choi u jong neimusah jing’e.
\v 18 Vo thaneipen Pathen, Kapu’u Abraham Pathen, Isaac Pathen, Israel te Pathen, namiten nathu angai jing ding uvin kahung tao’e. Nangma na jabol le na hepi nao jong mu jing’in.
\v 19 Kachapa Solomon’in alungthim pumpia nathupeh chengse anit a, na danthu le na hettohsah hihen, ejakai ajui jing’a, keiman kagontup pehsa na Hou-In theng kisahdoh kahsen lungvul na pejing o.
\v 20 Chuphat’in, David in mipi ho jah a, “Na Pakai, na Pathen’u thangvah un” ati.
\p Hichun, mipi jousen Pathen athangvah un,
\p Apu apateu Pathen masang’in abohkhup un, chibai abol uvin, lengpa jong jabolna apeuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Ajing nikhon, mipiten Pakaiya kilhainan Bongchal sangkhat, Kelngoi sangkhat le kelngoichal sangkhat ahin choijun, pumgo thilton atoh uve. Chujongleh, Israel pumpi min’in lengpitwi le kilhaina tampi jong ahin choi uvin ahi.
\v 22 Ann nehkhom abol’un, lengpitwi adon’un, Kipah le thanomtah in Pathen athangvah uve. Chujongleh, Leng David chapa Solomon chu mipi ho masang’in leng hung chang din thao anu un, Zadok jong chu thempu din thaonuna achangtai.
\s1 Solomon In Laltouna Aluo
\p 
\v 23 Chuin, Solomon in apa Leng David laltouna mun chu ahin khel tan, imalam jousea apa athakhel jou in, Israel pumpin jong ajabol sohkei taove. \x + \xo 29:23 \xt 1 Lgt 2:12\x*
\v 24 Mi thupiho, Gaalhang ho chuleh Leng David chapa te jousen jong Lengpa Solomon adin kitepna le kipehdohna anei taove.
\v 25 Chuban’a Pathen'in Leng Solomon chu Israel pumpi masang a adomsang’in, a itih a Israel lengten jong ana chan phahlou, minthanna, loupi na le jabolna sangpenin Pathen'in phatthei abohtai.
\v 26 Hitobanga hi, Jesse chapa Leng David hin jong Israel pumpin Lengvai ana pon ahi.
\v 27 A Lengvai poh chu kum somli alhing’in, kum sagi sung Hebron chuleh, kum \x + \xo 29:27 \xt 2 Samuel 5:4,5; 1 Thusimbu 3:4\x*
\p somthum le thum sung chu Jerusalem a lengvai ana po’i.
\p 
\v 28 Ahinkhon haona, jabolna achang’in, kum sottah hinkho kipah le thanom in amangin, atehset a ahinkho lhin mong’in athin, chuphat’in achapa Solomon in a Lengmun ahin khel e.
\v 29 Leng David vaipoh sungsea thil ejakai kijihlut ho jouse chu, a mitvaneipa Samuel thusimbu, Nathan themgaopa thusimle lekhabu, mitvaneipa Gad thusimbu a akijihlut soh in ahi.
\v 30 Hiche thilsoh ho jouse hin Leng David loupi na aphochen uvin, chuleh a lengvaipoh sung’a Israel le akimvel lenggam hoa thilsoh jouse jong ajao cheh e. 
